Upon arrival, the couple's weekend takes a bizarre, terrifying turn as a nightmarish cult and its maniacal leader terrorize the pair en route to fulfilling an ancient, apocalyptic prophecy.

Home.name: He's Out There
Home.description: On vacation at a remote lake house, a woman and her two young daughters fight to survive after falling into a terrifying and bizarre nightmare conceived by a psychopath.

Home.name: Grindhouse
Home.description: An ordinary evening in a small Texas town becomes a grisly nightmare when a horde of flesh-eating zombies goes on the prowl. Cherry (Rose McGowan), a go-go dancer, and Wray (Freddy Rodriguez), her ex-lover, band together with other survivors in a no-holds barred effort to escape the carnage. The odds become a bit more even when Cherry, who lost her leg to a hungry ghoul, gets a machine-gun appendage and lets the bullets fly.

Home.name: I, Frankenstein
Home.description: Adam, a monster created by Frankenstein, realises that his true calling is to save humanity after he finds himself in the middle of a war between the two immortal clans of demons and gargoyles.

Home.name: Devil in the Flesh
Home.description: When her mother is killed in a mysterious house fire, rebellious teen Debbie Strand (Rose McGowan) is sent to live with her grandmother (Peg Shirley), where she becomes even more unhinged. She develops an intense crush on her hunky creative writing teacher, Peter Rinaldi (Alex McArthur), but her numerous attempts at seduction end in failure. Soon Peter's friends start turning up dead, and he fears that his fiance, Marilyn (Sherrie Rose), may be Debbie's next victim.

Home.name: Scream VI
Home.description: Four survivors of the Ghostface murders leave Woodsboro behind for a fresh start in New York City. However, they soon find themselves in a fight for their lives when a new killer embarks on a bloody rampage.

Home.name: Blood
Home.description: When a bite from the family dog gives her son a horrific infection, a woman's morals get put to the test when the only cure to keep him alive proves deadly.

Home.name: Hush
Home.description: A deaf writer who retreated into the woods to live a solitary life must fight for her life in silence when a masked killer appears in her window.

Home.name: Consecration
Home.description: After the suspicious death of her brother, a priest, Grace travels to the Mount Saviour Convent in Scotland to find out what really happened. Once there, she uncovers murder, sacrilege and a disturbing truth about her own past.

Home.name: Silent Night
Home.description: A couple invite their closest friends to join their family for Christmas dinner at their idyllic home in the English countryside. As the group comes together, it feels like old times -- but behind all of the laughter and merriment, something isn't quite right. The world outside is facing impending doom, and no amount of gifts, games or wine can make mankind's imminent destruction go away. Surviving the holidays just got a lot more complicated.

Home.name: Evil Eye
Home.description: A seemingly perfect romance turns into a nightmare when a woman becomes convinced that her daughter's new boyfriend has a dark connection to her own past.

Home.name: Rampant
Home.description: Returning from imprisonment abroad, a prince and his fellow countrymen band together to battle bloodthirsty demons in ancient Korea.

Home.name: Aftermath
Home.description: Natalie and Kevin, a married couple, buy a house to renew and fix their marriage. However, their relationship strains further when they start experiencing strange phenomena in their new home.

Home.name: Piggy
Home.description: Sara is an overweight teen who witnesses a stranger kidnap a clique of girls who bully her on a regular basis. When police start asking questions, Sara keeps quiet as she's torn between revealing the truth or protecting the man who saved her.

Home.name: The Autopsy of Jane Doe
Home.description: A coroner and his son conduct an autopsy on a beautiful `Jane Doe' murder victim, and find increasingly bizarre clues.

Home.name: Cube
Home.description: A group of strangers awaken to find themselves placed in a giant cube. Each one of them is gifted with a special skill and they must work together to escape an endless maze of deadly traps.

Home.name: The Devil Conspiracy
Home.description: A powerful biotech company has breakthrough technology that allows it to clone history's most influential people. Behind this company is a cabal of Satanists who steal the shroud of Turin, putting them in possession of Jesus Christ's DNA -- the ultimate offering to the devil. Hoping to save mankind, Archangel Michael soon comes to Earth to stop the devil's conspiracy once and for all.

Home.name: The Devils
Home.description: In 17th-century France, Father Grandier (Oliver Reed) is a priest whose unorthodox views on sex and religion influence a passionate following of nuns, including the sexually obsessed Sister Jeanne (Vanessa Redgrave). When the power-hungry Cardinal Richelieu (Christopher Logue) realizes he must eliminate Grandier to gain control of France, Richelieu portrays Grandier as a satanist and spearheads a public outcry to destroy the once-loved priest's reputation.

Home.name: Unwelcome
Home.description: A couple escape their urban nightmare to the tranquility of rural Ireland, only to hear stories of mysterious creatures who live in the gnarled, ancient woods at the foot of their garden. As warned by their new neighbors, the creatures come when called to help souls in dire need of rescue, but it's crucial to remember that there's always a dear price to pay for their aid.

Home.name: Smile
Home.description: After witnessing a bizarre, traumatic incident involving a patient, Dr. Rose Cotter starts experiencing frightening occurrences that she can't explain. As an overwhelming terror begins taking over her life, Rose must confront her troubling past in order to survive and escape her horrifying new reality.

Home.name: Infinity Pool
Home.description: Guided by a seductive and mysterious woman, a couple on vacation venture outside the resort grounds and find themselves in a culture filled with violence, hedonism and untold horror. A tragic accident soon leaves them facing a zero tolerance policy for crime: either you'll be executed, or, if you're rich enough to afford it, you can watch yourself die instead.

Home.name: The Final Destination
Home.description: While watching a car race at a stadium with his friends, Nick has a premonition of a car crash which kills all the audience. However, he manages to save his friends. But how long can he cheat death.

Home.name: The Tenant
Home.description: In Paris, isolated Eastern European migr Trelkovsky (Roman Polanski) rents an apartment in a spooky old building whose inhabitants regard him with suspicion and even outright hostility. When he learns that the apartment's previous tenant, a beautiful woman, tried to commit suicide by jumping out the window, Trelkovsky begins to identify with her in increasingly disturbing ways. Then, to make matters even worse, he reaches the conclusion that his new neighbors are plotting to kill him.

Home.name: The Call
Home.description: Five years after the death of an old woman thought to be a witch, four friends meet and call the telephone installed in her casket. To their shock and horror, someone picks up.

Home.name: Anaconda (Hindi)
Home.description: A snake hunter offers his assistance to a documentary crew attempting to film an indigenous tribe in the Amazon. But as the journey progresses, his presence forces them to veer into dangerous waters.

Home.name: Burning Bright
Home.description: Kelly and his autistic brother Tom live with their stepfather Johnny. Johnny brings a tiger home for a project. This leaves Kelly and Tom in danger.

Home.name: Jennifer's Body
Home.description: Jennifer becomes possessed and turns into a succubus after she is sacrificed to Satan. When her best friend Anita learns about it, she has to stop Jennifer before she attacks her lover Chip.

Home.name: Barbarian
Home.description: A young woman discovers the rental home she booked is already occupied by a stranger. Against her better judgment, she decides to spend the night but soon discovers there's a lot more to fear than just an unexpected house guest.

Home.name: The Menu
Home.description: The film, penned by Will Tracy and Seth Reiss, "focuses on a young couple who visits an exclusive destination restaurant on a remote island where the acclaimed chef has prepared a lavish tasting menu, ...

Home.name: Knock at the Cabin
Home.description: While vacationing at a remote cabin in the woods, a young girl and her parents are taken hostage by four armed strangers who demand they make an unthinkable choice to avert the apocalypse. Confused, scared and with limited access to the outside world, the family must decide what they believe before all is lost.

Home.name: Sweeney Todd: The Demon Barber of Fleet Street
Home.description: Benjamin vows to seek revenge from the judge who framed him for a crime he did not commit. In order to do so, he reopens his barbershop and begins murdering his customers with a razor.

Home.name: Junglemahal: The Awakening
Home.description: Read allLoosely based on real incidents in the monsoon of mid 80s during the uprising of naxalites in eastern ghat range a group of travellers travels through the deep forests to reach the rescue camps. A series of mysterious incidents started taking place around them as the place is not what it seems.

Home.name: Run
Home.description: Chloe, a teenager, is forbidden from seeing the mail and is kept in isolation. She soon starts suspecting her mother of keeping dark secrets and decides to investigate.

Home.name: M3GAN
Home.description: M3GAN is a marvel of artificial intelligence, a lifelike doll that's programmed to be a child's greatest companion and a parent's greatest ally. Designed by Gemma, a brilliant roboticist, M3GAN can listen, watch and learn as it plays the role of friend and teacher, playmate and protector. When Gemma becomes the unexpected caretaker of her 8-year-old niece, she decides to give the girl an M3GAN prototype, a decision that leads to unimaginable consequences.

Home.name: The Twin
Home.description: Following the aftermath of a tragic accident that claimed the life of one of their twins, Rachel and Anthony relocate to the other side of the world with their surviving son. What begins as a time of healing in the quiet Scandinavian countryside soon takes an ominous turn when Rachel begins to unravel the torturous truth about her son and confronts the malicious forces that are trying to take hold of him.

Home.name: The Invitation
Home.description: After the death of her mother and having no other known relatives, Evie takes a DNA test and discovers a long-lost cousin she never knew she had. Invited by her newfound family to a lavish wedding in the English countryside, Evie's at first seduced by the sexy aristocratic host. However, she's soon thrust into a nightmare of survival as she uncovers twisted secrets about her family history and the unsettling intentions behind their sinful generosity.

Home.name: Primal
Home.description: Whilst swimming in the wild, an anthropology student regresses to an animal-like state and begins to hunt down her friends.

Home.name: Blurr
Home.description: Blurr is a 2022 Indian Hindi-language horror thriller film. It has been directed by Ajay Bahl and jointly produced by Zee Studios, Outsiders Films and Echelon Productions. The film features Taapsee Pannu and Gulshan Devaiah in the leading roles. This is Taapsee Pannu's first project as a producer.

Home.name: Bhediya
Home.description: Bhaskar finds himself changing after being bitten by a wolf in the forests of Arunachal. While Bhaskar begins to transform into a shape-shifting werewolf, he and his friends look for answers amid many twists, turns and laughs.

Home.name: Mr. Harrigan's Phone
Home.description: Craig, a young boy, befriends the elderly billionaire John Harrigan. Craig then gives him a mobile phone. However, when the man dies, Craig discovers that he can communicate with his friend from the grave.

Home.name: Orphan: First Kill
Home.description: After escaping from a psychiatric facility in Estonia, Esther travels to America by impersonating the missing daughter of a wealthy family. Yet, an unexpected twist arises that pits her against a mother who will protect her family at any cost.

Home.name: Nope
Home.description: A man and his sister discover something sinister in the skies above their California horse ranch, while the owner of a nearby theme park tries to profit from the mysterious, otherworldly phenomenon.

Home.name: Atithi Bhooto Bhava
Home.description: Atithi Bhooto Bhava is an Indian Hindi-language horror comedy film written by Aniket Wakchaure and directed by Hardik Gajjar. It features Jackie Shroff, Pratik Gandhi and Sharmin Segal in lead roles. The film went on floors in January 2021. It was released on ZEE5 on September 23, 2022.

Home.name: X
Home.description: A filmmaking crew and the cast make an adult movie at a reclusive place but elderly hosts find them and try to kill them.

Home.name: Incantation
Home.description: Six years ago, Li Ronan is cursed after breaking a religious taboo; now, she must protect her daughter from the consequences of her actions.

Home.name: The Sadness
Home.description: As Taiwan succumbs to a viral pandemic that transforms peaceful citizens into sadistic, bloodthirsty maniacs, a young couple must battle to be reunited before they too become infected.

Home.name: Jaws 2
Home.description: Post the shark attacks that horrified the residents of Amity, trouble returns to the town when a man-eating shark begins to lurk on the beaches of Amity.

Home.name: Train To Busan
Home.description: Seok-woo and his daughter are on a train to Busan on the latter's birthday to see his wife. However, the journey turns into a nightmare when they are trapped amidst a Zombie outbreak in South Korea.

Home.name: The Black Phone
Home.description: Finney Shaw is a shy but clever 13-year-old boy who's being held in a soundproof basement by a sadistic, masked killer. When a disconnected phone on the wall starts to ring, he soon discovers that he can hear the voices of the murderer's previous victims -- and they are dead set on making sure that what happened to them doesn't happen to Finney.

Home.name: Annabelle (Hindi)
Home.description: Judy and her babysitter are left alone in her house after her parents leave to investigate a case. However, an unexpected guest sets Annabelle free, unleashing demonic activity in the house.

Home.name: The Terminator
Home.description: It stars Arnold Schwarzenegger as the Terminator, a cyborg assassin sent back in time from 2029 to 1984 to kill Sarah Connor (Linda Hamilton), whose unborn son will one day save mankind from extinction by a hostile artificial intelligence in a post-apocalyptic future.

Home.name: Amavas
Home.description: Karan and Ahana's weekend vacation at an ancient palatial house turns into a nightmare when they are forced to fend themselves from the dark forces residing in the house.

Home.name: Bhool Bhulaiyaa
Home.description: An NRI and his wife decide to stay in his ancestral home, paying no heed to the warnings about ghosts. Soon, inexplicable occurrences cause him to call a psychiatrist to help solve the mystery.

Home.name: Wrong Turn 2: Dead End
Home.description: Participants of a reality show are tasked with surviving in a remote West Virginia forest. There, they encounter a family of deformed cannibals who want to slaughter them all and dine on human flesh.

Home.name: Resident Evil: Welcome to Raccoon City
Home.description: Welcome to Raccoon City, once the booming home of pharmaceutical giant UMBrella Corp. The company's exodus left the city a wasteland, a dying town with great evil brewing below the surface. When that evil is unleashed, a group of survivors must work together to uncover the truth behind UMBrella and make it through the night.

Home.name: Wrong Turn 3: Left for Dead
Home.description: A group of friends out on a hiking trip find themselves trapped in the woods, along with convicts from a nearby prison. Together they must fight against a gang of disfigured cannibals.

Home.name: Carrie 1976
Home.description: On the day of her prom night, seventeen-year-old Carrie discovers that she possesses telekinetic powers. She puts her powers to use when she is humiliated after a prank.

Home.name: It
Home.description: Seven helpless and bullied children are forced to face their worst nightmares when Pennywise, a shape-shifting clown, reappears. The clown, an ancient evil torments children before feeding on them.

Home.name: 1920: Evil Returns
Home.description: A famous poet, Jaidev, meets a woman who has lost her memories. He brings her to his house and tries to help her, but things take an ugly turn when she gets possessed by an evil spirit.

Home.name: Wrong Turn 5: Bloodlines
Home.description: A group of friends head out to attend a Halloween party in a distant town. Their plan goes awry when a family of cannibals attack them.

Home.name: Bhoot
Home.description: Swati and Vishal move into a new flat that is haunted by the spirit of its previous tenant. After a while, Vishal notices that Swati has started behaving in a strange manner.

Home.name: Death Note
Home.description: A high school student discovers a supernatural notebook that has deadly powers. He can kill anyone he wishes simply by inscribing their name within its pages. Intoxicated with his new power, he begins to eliminate those he deems unworthy of life.

Home.name: Piranha 3DD
Home.description: Piranha 3D is a 2010 American comedy-horror film that serves as a loose remake of the comedy horror film Piranha (1978) and an entry in the Piranha film series. During spring break on Lake Victoria, a popular waterside resort, an underground tremor releases hundreds of prehistoric, carnivorous piranhas into the lake.

Home.name: Sinister
Home.description: Ellison, a crime writer, moves his family to a house that once witnessed gruesome murders. Soon, when his research leads him to some eerie footage, things take a dark and harrowing turn.

Home.name: I Am Legend
Home.description: Robert Neville, a scientist, is the last human survivor of a plague in the whole of New York. He attempts to find a way to reverse the effects of the man-made virus by using his own immune blood.

Home.name: The Nun
Home.description: A priest and a novice arrive in Romania to investigate the death of a young nun. However, things take an ugly turn after they encounter a supernatural force.

Home.name: The Car
Home.description: When a series of people are murdered in Utah by a mysterious black car, Sheriff Wade Parent sets out to investigate the case. Soon he realises that he must deal with supernatural powers.

Home.name: Wrong Turn (English)
Home.description: Chris and a group of five friends are left stranded deep in the middle of the woods after their cars collide. As they venture deeper into the woods, they face an uncertain and bloodcurdling fate.

Home.name: Evil Dead (Hindi)
Home.description: Five friends decide to spend a weekend in a remote cabin located deep in the forest. When they accidentally summon a dormant demon, they strive to survive its evil ploys.

Home.name: The Babysitter: Killer Queen
Home.description: Two years after defeating a satanic cult led by his babysitter Bee, Cole once again has to outsmart the forces of evil when old enemies unexpectedly return.

Home.name: Boo 2! A Madea Halloween
Home.description: Madea, Bam, and Hattie find themselves in trouble when they encounter monsters, goblins and boogeyman at a haunted campsite.

Home.name: Truth or dare
Home.description: A group of friends who are lured into a game of truth or dare realise that the ones who lie or do not follow the rules, end up dead, mysteriously.

Home.name: Wrong Turn 4: Bloody Beginnings
Home.description: A group of friends take refuge in a deserted sanatorium after they are left stranded in a snowstorm. Later, the place becomes a death trap when man-eating cannibals surround them.

Home.name: Evil Dead (English)
Home.description: Five friends decide to spend a weekend in a remote cabin located deep in the forest. When they accidentally summon a dormant demon, they strive to survive its evil ploys.

Home.name: Bhoot Police
Home.description: Two brothers, Vibhooti and Chiraunji, have fought their share of ghosts. A new case forces them to rethink their own abilities and beliefs.

Home.name: Queen of the Damned
Home.description: Vampire Lestat awakens from his sluMBer and becomes a rock star. But chaos strikes when his music awakens Akasha, the vampire queen, who will not rest until she makes Lestat her new king.

Home.name: Ghost Stories
Home.description: The winning team of LUST STORIES unite to tell some spine - chilling tales. Ghost Stories is an upcoming 2020 Indian anthology horror film, consisting of four short film segments.

Home.name: World War Z
Home.description: Gerry, a former United Nations employee, unexpectedly finds himself in a race against time as he investigates a threatening virus that turns humans into Zombies.

Home.name: Mushkil
Home.description: Four friends vacationing at a guest house in Greece are compelled to seek help from Vedant, a handsome tour guide, and Aveer, a mysterious man, after experiencing a series of paranormal events.

Home.name: Annabelle
Home.description: Judy and her babysitter are left alone in her house after her parents leave to investigate a case. However, an unexpected guest sets Annabelle free, unleashing demonic activity in the house.

Home.name: I Spit on Your Grave
Home.description: Jennifer (Sarah Butler), a writer, rents an isolated cabin in the country so she can work on her latest novel. The peace and quiet is soon shattered by a gang of local thugs who rape and torture her, then leave her for dead. But she returns for vengeance, trapping the men one by one. Jennifer inflicts pain on her attackers with a ferocity that surpasses her own ordeal.

Home.name: The Possession of Hannah Grace
Home.description: A demon seeks refuge in a young girl's body when she dies due to an unruly exorcism. Later, her corpse is moved to a morgue guarded by a former officer who experiences unnatural events.

Home.name: Ragini MMS 2
Home.description: A director attempts to shoot an erotic horror movie in a house where, unbeknown to him, a demonic spirit resides. Even before the crew starts filming, the spirit possesses the lead actress's body.

Home.name: The Conjuring 2
Home.description: Peggy, a single mother of four children, seeks the help of occult investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren when she and her children witness strange, paranormal events in their house.

Home.name: Carrie
Home.description: Carrie, an awkward teenager protected by fanatical mother, becomes the butt of all jokes in school. When the pranks of her classmates go out of hand, she unleashes her telekinetic powers.

Home.name: Let the Right One In
Home.description: When Oskar (Kre Hedebrant), a sensitive, bullied 12-year-old boy living with his mother in suburban Sweden, meets his new neighbor, the mysterious and moody Eli (Lina Leandersson), they strike up a friendship. Initially reserved with each other, Oskar and Eli slowly form a close bond, but it soon becomes apparent that she is no ordinary young girl. Eventually, Eli shares her dark, macabre secret with Oskar, revealing her connection to a string of bloody local murders.

Home.name: Roohi
Home.description: Bhawra and Kattanni kidnap Roohi on the orders of Guniya Bhai, who wants to marry her off to his client. However, things take a paranormal turn when they realise that Roohi is possessed by a demon.

Home.name: Ek Thi Daayan
Home.description: Bobo, a famous magician, plans to marry his girlfriend. However, he is secretly scarred by persistent hallucinations of his dead sister and is forced to seek psychiatric help.

Home.name: Laxmii
Home.description: Aasif visits his wife's parents' house and happens to go to a ground that is supposedly haunted. However, he is soon possessed by the spirit of a transgender who is out for revenge.

Home.name: Ouija (English)
Home.description: When Debbie is found dead after playing with an Ouija board, her best friend, Laine, decides to communicate with her using the board. Things go awry when she contacts an evil spirit instead.

Home.name: Ouija (Hindi)
Home.description: When Debbie is found dead after playing with an Ouija board, her best friend, Laine, decides to communicate with her using the board. Things go awry when she contacts an evil spirit instead.

Home.name: The Curse of La Llorona
Home.description: When Patricia is found endangering the lives of her sons, Anna puts her behind bars. However, when Anna's own children are endangered, she suspects that there is more than human involvement at play.

Home.name: Veronica
Home.description: During a solar eclipse, a teenage girl and her friends want to summon the spirit of the girl's father using an Ouija board. However, during the session she loses consciousness and soon it becomes clear that evil demons have arrived.

Home.name: 47 meters down
Home.description: A vacation turns into a disaster after two sisters, Lisa and Kate, are trapped in a diving cage underwater with predatorial sharks circling them.

Home.name: The Ring
Home.description: After her niece Katie's horrifying death, Rachel, a young journalist, investigates a mysterious videotape that kills its viewers within a week's time.

Home.name: Beloved
Home.description: Sethe is a former slave who lives with her daughter Denver, together they experience strange things in the house after the visit of a young woman, whose existence brings their past fears to life.

Home.name: The Green Inferno
Home.description: Justine and Alejandro are among the survivors of a plane that has crashed in a jungle in Peru. Things take a turn for the worse when they get abducted by a tribe of cannibals.

Home.name: The Invisible Man
Home.description: Cecilia's abusive ex-boyfriend fakes his death and becomes invisible to stalk and torment her. She begins experiencing strange events and decides to hunt down the truth on her own.

Home.name: The Ring Two
Home.description: After the ordeal with Samara, Rachel and Aiden move to a rural town. But soon Rachel learns about the death of a girl in a similar fashion. To save Aiden, she must dig into Samara's past even further.

Home.name: Ouija: Origin of Evil
Home.description: A widow and her two daughters use an Ouija board to help people move on with life. They interact with a spirit but are unaware of the fact that it has possessed Doris, the youngest daughter.

Home.name: Van Helsing (English)
Home.description: Van Helsing, a legendary monster hunter, is sent to Transylvania in order to prevent Count Dracula, a terrorising being, from realising his evil motives.

Home.name: Van Helsing (Hindi)
Home.description: Van Helsing, a legendary monster hunter, is sent to Transylvania in order to prevent Count Dracula, a terrorising being, from realising his evil motives.

Home.name: Lake of Death
Home.description: Together with a group of friends, Liljan returns to the family cabin where his twin brother Bjrn died the year before. They will finally say goodbye and make the cabin ready for sale. But soon strange things begin to happen.

Home.name: Anacondas: The Hunt for the Blood Orchid
Home.description: A large corporation sponsors a team of biologists to travel deep into the Amazon rainforest and retrieve a flower known as blood orchid, which could hold the key to everlasting youth.

Home.name: The Conjuring
Home.description: The Perron family moves into a farmhouse where they experience paranormal phenomena. They consult demonologists, Ed and Lorraine Warren, to help them get rid of the evil entity haunting them.

Home.name: Dhilluku Dhuddu
Home.description: Kumar and Kajal are in love but her father is against the match and tries to have Kumar killed with the help of Mani. Things go awry when Mani invites Kumar's family to a haunted house.

Home.name: Underworld
Home.description: Selene, a vampire orphaned due to a deadly werewolf attack, works for a vampire clan as a trained murderer. She battles to save Michael, a skilled human doctor, from the machinations of werewolves.

Home.name: Spiral
Home.description: When a policeman is murdered by a Jigsaw copycat killer, Zeke Banks is assigned to investigate the case. In the process of punishing the perpetrator, he ends up facing the demons of his past.

Home.name: Cannibal Holocaust
Home.description: During a rescue mission into the Amazon rainforest, a professor stuMBles across lost film shot by a missing documentary crew whose goal was to study the region's indigenous cannibalistic tribes.

Home.name: Go Goa Gone
Home.description: While in Goa, three friends decide to visit an isolated island for a rave party. But the next morning they find themselves not only stranded but also surrounded and hunted by flesh-eating Zombies.

Home.name: Jigsaw
Home.description: The police are at a dead end when investigating numerous ghastly murders in the city that reseMBles the work of a serial killer who is known to be dead since ten years.

Home.name: Eerie
Home.description: A guidance counsellor's special talents help her unravel the mystery behind the unexpected and gruesome death of a student at a Catholic school for girls.

Home.name: The Conjuring (Hindi)
Home.description: The Perron family moves into a farmhouse where they experience paranormal phenomena. They consult demonologists, Ed and Lorraine Warren, to help them get rid of the evil entity haunting them.

Home.name: Wrong Turn 6: Last Resort
Home.description: After arriving at Hobb Springs, Danny and his friends are exposed to a series of harrowing incidents and are attacked by three cannibal brothers, Saw Tooth, One Eye and Three Finger.

Home.name: Orphan
Home.description: After losing their baby, a couple adopt a nine-year-old girl. However, they soon make a troubling discovery about her mysterious past and uncover several traits of her disturbing personality.

Home.name: A Haunted House
Home.description: Young couple Malcolm (Marlon Wayans) and Kisha (Essence Atkins) have just moved into their dream home. As they settle in, they learn that they're not alone -- not because the house is haunted, but because Kisha is possessed by a demon. Desperate to salvage his relationship -- and more importantly -- his sex life -- Malcolm hires a coterie of paranormal specialists, which includes a priest and ghost busters, to banish the unwelcome intruder from Kisha's body.

Home.name: Khamoshiyan
Home.description: Kabir, a struggling writer, travels to Kashmir for inspiration and starts staying at a mysterious guest house. He falls in love with Meera, the owner of the guesthouse, who harbours a dark secret.

Home.name: American Mary
Home.description: Medical student Mary Mason is lured into a world of performing freakish surgeries to earn money for school.

Home.name: Orphan (Hindi)
Home.description: After losing their baby, a couple adopt a nine-year-old girl. However, they soon make a troubling discovery about her mysterious past and uncover several traits of her disturbing personality.

Home.name: The Exorcist
Home.description: Regan, a young girl, displays bizarre behaviour after playing with a Ouija board. Chris, her mother and an actress, consults two priests who conclude that Regan is possessed by a demonic entity.

Home.name: The Conjuring 3
Home.description: Arne Cheyenne Johnson stabs and murders his landlord, claiming to be under demonic possession. Ed and Lorraine Warren investigate the case and try to prove his innocence.

Home.name: Annabelle: Creation
Home.description: Samuel and Elle eMBed their daughter's spirit into a doll, only to realise it is a demon. Years later, they open their home to a nun and six orphan girls, one of whom finds the doll.

Home.name: Annabelle Comes Home
Home.description: Judy and her babysitter are left alone in her house after her parents leave to investigate a case. However, an unexpected guest sets Annabelle free, unleashing demonic activity in the house.

Home.name: Mo
Home.description: Three friends fool people into believing they are exorcists and take money from them under false pretences. But when they get hired to scare a business rival, they encounter a real spirit.

Home.name: Trauma
Home.description: A relaxing weekend in the countryside turns bloody for a group of women when a deranged man and his sadistic son brutally attack them.

Home.name: Holidays
Home.description: Nine filmmakers present horror stories that revolve around eight different holidays: Valentine's Day, Saint Patrick's Day, Easter, Mother's Day, Father's Day, Halloween, Christmas and New Year's Eve.

Home.name: Life
Home.description: As astronauts discover the first evidence of extra-terrestrial life on Mars, they begin realising that the life form is extremely intelligent and hostile.

Home.name: Raju Gari Gadhi 2
Home.description: Three friends decide to invest in a resort and run a business. When they learn that a series of paranormal activities takes place, they seek help from a renowned mentalist.

Home.name: 13B: Fear Has a New Address

Home.description: Amar and Prem, who belong to middle-class families, compete to win over Raveena, a millionaire's daughter. Along the way, they run into a local gangster, Teja, who turns their lives upside down.

Home.name: Her
Home.description: Theodore Twombly, an introverted writer, buys an Artificial Intelligence system to help him write. However, when he finds out about the AI's ability to learn and adapt, he falls in love with it.

Home.name: Cleopatra
Home.description: Cleopatra, the queen of Egypt, becomes the mistress of Julius Ceaser of Rome in order to save her kingdom. However, when Ceaser is assassinated, she becomes Mark Antony's ally and lover.

Home.name: The Piano
Home.description: After a long voyage from Scotland, pianist Ada McGrath (Holly Hunter) and her young daughter, Flora (Anna Paquin), are left with all their belongings, including a piano, on a New Zealand beach. Ada, who has been mute since childhood, has been sold into marriage to a local man named Alisdair Stewart (Sam Neill). Making little attempt to warm up to Alisdair, Ada soon becomes intrigued by his Maori-friendly acquaintance, George Baines (Harvey Keitel), leading to tense, life-altering conflicts.

Home.name: Body Heat
Home.description: Shyster lawyer Ned Racine (William Hurt) begins a passionate affair with Matty Walker (Kathleen Turner), wife of a wealthy Florida businessman (Richard Crenna). With the help of one of his criminal clients, bomb maker Teddy Lewis (Mickey Rourke), Ned hatches a scheme to kill Matty's husband so that they can run away together with his money. But complications build upon double-crosses, launching the hapless lawyer into a situation far more treacherous than he imagined.

Home.name: Honeymoon
Home.description: After consenting to an arranged marriage, Praveen and Tejaswini embark on a journey filled with unexpected events and emotions, and their unplanned honeymoon turns out to be their best decision yet.

Home.name: Yes Man
Home.description: Carl, a lonely man with low self-esteem, participates in a self-help programme that challenges him to say yes to everything in life for an entire year.

Home.name: G.I. Blues
Home.description: McLean (Elvis Presley) dreams of running his own nightclub when he leaves the army and places a bet on his friend to spend a night with the most popular club dancer named Lili.

Home.name: Anna Karenina
Home.description: Aristocrat Anna Karenina, a married woman with a young son, meets Count Vronsky while visiting her brother. Their mutual attraction leads her to grief and tragedy.

Home.name: When Night Is Falling
Home.description: Camille (Pascale Bussires) is a mythology lecturer at a conservative Christian college. She's engaged to be married and is on the path to a stable career. But, when her dog dies, Camille finds her life unraveling. At a low ebb, she crosses paths with fiery circus performer Petra (Rachael Crawford) in a laundromat, and sparks fly. With Petra pursuing her ardently, Camille experiences a sexual awakening and must confront the daunting prospect of changing her entire existence.

Home.name: Come Play with Me
Home.description: Come Play with Me is a 1977 British softcore pornographic film, starring Mary Millington and directed by George Harrison Marks. Its cast list contains many well-known British character actors who were not known for appearing in such films.

Home.name: Titanic (Hindi)
Home.description: Seventeen-year-old Rose hails from an aristocratic family and is set to be married. When she boards the Titanic, she meets Jack Dawson, an artist, and falls in love with him.

Home.name: The Painted Veil
Home.description: Dr Walter gets married to the beautiful Kitty but soon finds out that she is cheating on him. Battling his way through life, he heads to China to fight a dreaded disease that has spread in a village.

Home.name: Mumbai Pune Mumbai 3
Home.description: Gautam and Gauri, an ambitious couple, are happily married and decide to focus on their careers. But an unplanned pregnancy causes conflict between them and their families.

Home.name: On a Magical Night
Home.description: After 20 years of marriage, Maria decides to leave her home, go to the hotel across the street and contemplate her life.

Home.name: The Concubine
Home.description: To escape a life of poverty, Hwa-yeon becomes one of the king's concubines and two men become captivated by her.

Home.name: Natalie
Home.description: A dance student who has fallen out of love with her lover leaves for her fellow student. Years later the two meet and share conflicting memories of her.

Home.name: Close My Eyes
Home.description: Richard (Clive Owen) is a confident Londoner who has always had a slightly unconventional relationship with his beautiful yet insecure sister, Natalie (Saskia Reeves). When their oddly flirtatious behavior crosses the line into an incestuous affair, it creates significant problems for both of them, especially when Natalie's husband, Sinclair (Alan Rickman), suspects something is amiss. As Natalie tries to call off her trysts with Richard, he becomes increasingly unhinged.

Home.name: The Nutty Professor
Home.description: Sherman, an extremely overweight genetics professor, falls in love with a colleague. But when he experiments on himself with a slimming potion, it not only trims him down but also makes him obnoxious.

Home.name: Serve the People
Home.description: Serve the People is a 2022 South Korean romantic drama film, written and directed by Jang Cheol-soo and starring Yeon Woo-jin, Ji An, Jo Sung-ha and Kim Ji-chul.

Home.name: Legend
Home.description: Identical twins Reggie and Ronnie Kray rise through the ranks of the criminal underworld to become two of London's most dreaded gangsters.

Home.name: Barfi!
Home.description: Barfi forms a special bond with Jhilmil, a girl with autism. When Barfi's old flame walks back into his life, it causes misunderstandings between Jhilmil and him.

Home.name: Jaggu Ani Juliet
Home.description: Jaggu Ani Juliet is a 2023 Indian Marathi-language Romantic Comedy film directed by Mahesh Limaye. It is produced by Punit Balan Studios.

Home.name: Dulhan Hum Le Jayenge
Home.description: Sapna is raised by her three uncles, each one of them with a contrasting pursuit in life. She falls in love with Raja, who tries to impress each of her uncles in a different manner.

Home.name: Mujhse Dosti Karoge!
Home.description: Raj falls in love with Tina after their friendship blossoms via emails. However, he is unaware that Tina's best friend, Pooja, is the one writing these mails.

Home.name: Blast from the Past
Home.description: Adam Weber ventures out on the streets of Los Angeles after being trapped in a bomb shelter for thirty-five years. In his search for food and supplies, he meets Eve, who agrees to help him.

Home.name: Middle Class Love
Home.description: Unhappy with his family's middle-class lifestyle, young Yudi assumes that joining a renowned college and having a wealthy girlfriend are the best ways to escape it.

Home.name: Loev
Home.description: Lives are upended when a hiking trip leads a Wall Street hotshot to explore his true feelings for an old friend who's disenchanted with his boyfriend.

Home.name: Tu Jhoothi Main Makkaar
Home.description: Tu Jhoothi Main Makkaar, also abbreviated as TJMM, is a 2023 Indian Hindi-language romantic comedy film directed by Luv Ranjan and written by Rahul Mody, Luv Ranjan.

Home.name: Beyond Borders
Home.description: A married woman comes across a renegade doctor and decides to aid him on his relief mission in war-torn Africa. The two set out on a journey of danger, adventures and love.

Home.name: My Fair Lady
Home.description: In this beloved musical, pompous phonetics professor Henry Higgins (Rex Harrison) is so sure of his abilities that he takes it upon himself to transform a Cockney working-class girl into someone who can pass for a cultured member of high society. His subject turns out to be the lovely Eliza Doolittle (Audrey Hepburn), who agrees to speech lessons to improve her job prospects. Higgins and Eliza clash, then form an unlikely bond -- one that is threatened by an aristocratic suitor (Jeremy Brett).

Home.name: Ryan's Daughter
Home.description: A behind-the-scenes look at the making of the film 'Ryan's Daughter' starring Robert Mitchum, Trevor Howard, Christopher Jones, Sarah Miles and directed by David Lean.

Home.name: Swept Away
Home.description: A haughty rich housewife and her shipmate get stranded in a thunderstorm. Suddenly, the rules governing their relationship change when she has to depend on her shipmate for survival.

Home.name: Every Day
Home.description: Rhiannon, a teenage girl, falls in love with a spirit that inhabits a different person's body every day. Soon, their life changes drastically as they face a difficult decision.

Home.name: The Tenant
Home.description: A conservative Mumbai suburb is bestirred by the arrival of an alluring cosmopolitan woman in their midst. When a wide-eyed 13-year-old boy pursues a friendship with her, he stumbles upon her secret past and is thrust headlong into adulthood.

Home.name: The Merchant of Venice
Home.description: Bassanio requires a lot of money if he wants to marry Portia. Unable to procure it from elsewhere, he must make a deadly deal with Shylock, a cruel moneylender from the Semitic ghetto.

Home.name: Nautanki Saala!
Home.description: Ram, a successful theatre artist, saves Mandar from committing suicide. He then ends up developing a special bond with Mandar and even helps solve his problems.

Home.name: Unfreedom
Home.description: A Muslim terrorist kidnaps a liberal Muslim scholar and a young woman resists her devout father's efforts to force her into an arranged marriage in two brutal stories of fundamentalism and intolerance.

Home.name: Ninnila Ninnila
Home.description: Dev, a cook, meets Tara, a young woman, and soon love blossoms between them. However, he is unable to let go of his past, which haunts him in the form of hallucinations.

Home.name: The Reader
Home.description: Michael, a teenager, falls in love with an older woman named Hanna. Their liaison ends when she suddenly vanishes. They meet after a decade when she goes on trial for being a Nazi guard during WWII.

Home.name: Punish Me
Home.description: Elsa, a probation officer, finds herself more and more attracted to a 16 year old offender who offers to submit himself sexually to her.

Home.name: All Things Fair
Home.description: Stig (Johan Widerberg) is 15 years old and lives in neutral Sweden while the rest of the world is swept up in World War II. Like many other boys in his school, he's in love with biology teacher Viola (Marika Lagercrantz), but, unlike other boys, he secretly starts seeing her. Viola confesses to Stig that he provides her with much-needed comfort since her marriage to Kjell (Tomas von Brmssen), a drunk, is falling apart. Their relationship grows complicated when Kjell discovers their affair.

Home.name: Leaving
Home.description: A bourgeois housewife, planning to go back to work as a physiotherapist after having devoted 20 years to her husband and two children, has her comfortable, elegant life turned upside down when she falls for a Spanish builder and begins a runaway affair.

Home.name: Your Place or Mine
Home.description: Debbie and Peter are best friends and total opposites. She craves routine with her son in LA, but he thrives on change in NY. When they swap houses and lives for a week they discover what they think they want might not be what they really need.

Home.name: Swann in Love
Home.description: In 19th-century Paris, Charles Swann (Jeremy Irons) risks his social standing in his obsessive pursuit of prostitute Odette (Ornella Muti). His overwhelming desire for her comes, in part, from Odette's complete disinterest in him. When he finally weds her, utterly compromising himself in high society, he finds to his horror that his love for her was a complete illusion. At the same time, the Baron de Charlus (Alain Delon) pursues his own ill-advised romance.

Home.name: London
Home.description: When Syd, a drug addict, learns about his ex-girlfriend London's farewell party, he decides to gatecrash the event in order to win her back.

Home.name: Two Moon Junction
Home.description: Two Moon Junction is a 1988 American erotic thriller romance film written and directed by Zalman King and starring Sherilyn Fenn and Richard Tyson. The original music score is composed by Jonathan Elias. Two Moon Junction.

Home.name: Unfaithful
Home.description: Connie, a married woman, bumps into Paul, a handsome stranger, and finds herself attracted to him. However, when she pursues an extramarital affair with him, Edward, her husband, gets suspicious.

Home.name: The Shape Of Water (Hindi)
Home.description: Elisa, a lonely janitor, stuMBles upon an amphibious creature that is held captive in a secret research facility. She then develops a unique relationship with the creature.

Home.name: In Her Shoes
Home.description: Rose, a successful but lonely attorney, breaks relations with her party-going irresponsible sister, Maggie. Soon, the arrival of their grandmother, whom they don't remember, brings them closer.

Home.name: Good Will Hunting
Home.description: Will Hunting, a genius in mathematics, solves all the difficult mathematical problems. When he faces an emotional crisis, he takes help from psychiatrist Dr Sean Maguireto, who helps him recover.

Home.name: Jaan
Home.description: Police Commissioner Suryadeo Singh hires Karan, a trained weapons expert, to protect his daughter Kajal. Later, Kajal, who is unaware of Karan's secret mission, falls in love with him.

Home.name: Koogle Kuttappa
Home.description: A conservative villager hates the idea of his son relocating to Russia for a job. However, when his son brings a robot to care for him, he develops an unlikely bond with the machine.

Home.name: Sita Ramam
Home.description: Upon returning to Pakistan, Afreen sets off to fulfil her grandfather's wish of delivering a letter from Ram to Sita. Along the way, she finds Ram and learns about their love story.

Home.name: Chhatriwali
Home.description: Chhatriwali is a 2023 Indian Hindi-language Romantic comedy film directed by Tejas Deoskar and produced by Ronnie Screwvala. The film stars an Rakul Preet Singh, Sumeet Vyas, Satish Kaushik, Dolly Ahluwalia and Rajesh Tailang. The film was premiered on 20 January 2023 on ZEE5.

Home.name: Aum Mangalam Singlem
Home.description: Aum Mangalam Singlem is a 2022 Gujarati romantic comedy film directed by Saandeep Patel. It stars and Malhar Thakar, Aarohi Patel, Bhamini Oza Gandhi, Darshan Jariwala and Nisarg Trivedi in lead roles.

Home.name: Tadka
Home.description: Tadka is an Indian Hindi-language romantic comedy-drama film directed by actor Prakash Raj, starring Nana Patekar, Ali Fazal, Shriya Saran and Tapsee Pannu. The story of the film is based in Goa and filming began in May 2016. It is a remake of the 2011 Malayalam film Salt N' Pepper.

Home.name: Laal Singh Chaddha
Home.description: A simple man with a disability embarks on an extraordinary journey, meeting many friends along the way.

Home.name: Purple Hearts
Home.description: Cassie, a struggling singer-songwriter agrees to marry a troubled Marine, Luke for military benefits. The line between real and pretend begins to blur.

Home.name: Persuasion
Home.description: When Frederick Wentworth -- the one who got away -- crashes back into Anne Elliot's life, she must choose between putting the past behind her or listening to her heart when it comes to second chances.

Home.name: Paglu 2
Home.description: Dev, a high-school dropout, relocates to the city in order to finish his studies. Soon, he falls in love with a girl in his college but things go awry when she is kidnapped by a group of hoodlums.

Home.name: Jodhaa Akbar
Home.description: Jodhaa is a fiery Rajput princess who is obliged to marry Mughal Emperor Akbar for political reasons. Eventually, mutual respect and admiration between the duo leads to true love.

Home.name: Judaa Hoke Bhi
Home.description: Judaa Hoke Bhi is a 2022 Indian supernatural-horror film written by Mahesh Bhatt and directed by Vikram Bhatt and produced by Loneranger Productions and Houseful Motion Pictures.

Home.name: Father of the Bride
Home.description: A father must come to grips with his daughter's upcoming wedding and handle multiple relationships within his sprawling Cuban American family.

Home.name: The Digital Thief
Home.description: An honest police officer is tasked with taping the calls of elite professionals by a senior official. On the job, he learns about an online sociopath and sets out to expose him.

Home.name: Karan Arjun
Home.description: Durga's two sons, Karan and Arjun, set out to avenge their father's death, only to get themselves killed by their evil uncle. Years later, the two are reincarnated to bring justice.

Home.name: Nikamma
Home.description: A man and his new sister-in-law must put aside their differences when they find themselves in a brutal, lawless town.

Home.name: The Sun Is Also A Star
Home.description: Natasha, a pragmatic woman from Jamaica, falls in love with Daniel, an equivocal medical student, under atypical circumstances. However, their relationship is challenged by their own destiny.

Home.name: Total Dadagiri
Home.description: College students Joy and Jonaki fall in love with each other, much to the distress of her father, who is totally opposed to their relationship.

Home.name: Something New
Home.description: Pursuing a career has made Kenya's life dull, or so believe her friends who set her up for a blind date. But when Brian turns out to be white, Kenya backs off, not knowing that cupid will strike soon.

Home.name: Aiyyaa
Home.description: An eccentric woman, Meenakshi, meets Surya, a Tamil artist, and is instantly attracted to him. Even when she gets engaged to Madhav, the ideal man, she still dreams of marrying Surya.

Home.name: Lekh
Home.description: During their teen years, Rajvir and Ronak are attracted to one another but never act on their feelings. As years go on and they drift apart, they are reunited by fate and rediscover their attraction.

Home.name: Thanks For Sharing
Home.description: A recovering sex addict (Mark Ruffalo) tries not to fall off the wagon as he woos a new girlfriend (Gwyneth Paltrow) who feels the need to express her rampant sexuality.

Home.name: Kanamachi
Home.description: Abir, a photojournalist, extends his support to Abhimanyu, a rising politician. However, he soon comes across some disturbing revelations about the Naxals and their influence on the local politics.

Home.name: Lover
Home.description: Charitha, a doctor, endangers her life when she saves a child from being kidnapped for her liver. Later, Raj, who is in love with Charitha, protects her when goons try to kill her.

Home.name: Khoka 420
Home.description: Krish is the son of a rich man and is in love with Megha. However, things become complicated when Megha's best friend, Bhoomi, enters their lives and falls in love with Krish.

Home.name: Saunkan Saunkne
Home.description: Married for many years, Nirmal and Naseeb have lost all hope of having a child. Naseeb persuades Nirmal to marry her younger sister, but sharing her husband proves more difficult than she thought.

Home.name: Over Her Dead Body
Home.description: Kate turns into a ghost after she dies on the day of her wedding. She then decides to sabotage her ex-fiance's new relationship with a psychic.

Home.name: Malaal
Home.description: In a chawl in MuMBai, Shiva and Astha fall in love despite the differences in their backgrounds. However, various circumstances threaten to tear them apart.

Home.name: Fifty Shades Of Grey
Home.description: Anastasia fills in for her journalist friend and interviews Christian Grey, a businessman. They begin a relationship where she discovers that his sexual life is influenced by his tormented past.

Home.name: Ae Dil Hai Mushkil
Home.description: Alizeh, an independent woman recovering from a breakup, and Ayan, a naive musician, meet in New York and form an incredible bond. From there, they experience love, heartbreak and the facts of life.

Home.name: Yeh Saali Aashiqui
Home.description: A supposedly deranged man is arrested on suspicion of breaking into his ex-lover's home. But when he starts talking, he appears to be far more intelligent and twisted than anyone could have predicted.

Home.name: Your Name.
Home.description: Two teenagers share a profound, magical connection upon discovering they are swapping bodies. Things manage to become even more complicated when the boy and girl decide to meet in person.

Home.name: Pride & Prejudice
Home.description: Mrs Bennet insists that her daughters find rich husbands and settle down. When a wealthy bachelor starts living near them, Mrs Bennet's happiness knows no bounds.

Home.name: Roy
Home.description: Kabir, a casanova film-maker, meets a London-based director, Ayesha, and falls in love with her. Elsewhere, an international art thief decides to be a better person after falling for a woman.

Home.name: Mapla Singam
Home.description: Amidst the rivalry of two castes in a village, a leader's daughter falls in love with a boy from the rival caste. Things take a turn when her cousin Anbu falls in love with the boy's sister.

Home.name: Besharam
Home.description: Babli is a small-time thief who steals cars in order to support a noble cause. His life takes an interesting turn when he falls in love with Tara and decides to mend his ways.

Home.name: Maharshi
Home.description: A rich businessman returns to India to mend ways with his ex-classmate. However, when he learns about his friend's plight, he tries to help him and becomes a saviour for the villagers in the process.

Home.name: Amavas
Home.description: Karan and Ahana's weekend vacation at an ancient palatial house turns into a nightmare when they are forced to fend themselves from the dark forces residing in the house.

Home.name: Love, Rosie
Home.description: Rosie and Alex have been friends since childhood and cannot imagine themselves as a couple. However, when they head in different directions, they realise that they are made for each other.

Home.name: Heartbeat
Home.description: Thelma's (Ruth Kadiri) marriage suffer hitches because of several cases of domestic violence, Her husband, Mike (Frederick Leonard) became her nightmare, Despite plea from friends and relatives Thelma refuse to call it quit with her marriage, her mother Inlaw's advice further gave her the courage to hold on in her bid to cure her husband of the dreaded psychological ailments that leads to domestic abuses.

Home.name: Anjaana Anjaani
Home.description: Akash and Kiara, two heartbroken and suicidal people, find each other just as they are about to end their lives. The duo then decide to live life to the fullest until New Year's Day.

Home.name: Tanu Weds Manu Returns
Home.description: After Tanu and Manu's marriage falls apart, the latter finds himself smitten by Datto, a lookalike of his ex-wife. But soon enough, the estranged couple's feelings begin to spark again.

Home.name: Surya The Soldier
Home.description: A soldier aspiring to be posted at the LOC suffers from anger management issues, due to which he gets court-martialled. He then sets out to meet a psychologist whose approval can get him back on duty.

Home.name: The Girl Next Door
Home.description: Matthew, a high school senior, thinks that he has found the woman of his dreams. However, he soon learns that Danielle, the object of his affection, is a former adult film actress.

Home.name: After Everything
Home.description: Elliot is a young and carefree New Yorker whose world gets turned upside down when he finds out that he has cancer. He soon finds comfort and happiness when he falls in love with Mia, a woman who sticks with him through the hard times.

Home.name: Ferris Bueller's Day Off
Home.description: Ferris Bueller, a high school student, fakes sickness to stay at home and spends the rest of the day with his best friend and girlfriend. Meanwhile, his dean tries to spy on him.

Home.name: 21 Jump Street
Home.description: Schmidt and Jenko are high school friends who go on to become police officers. The two friends go undercover as students in order to bust a drug ring and find the source of a synthetic drug.

Home.name: Soppana Sundari
Home.description: A struggling middle-class family wins a car in a raffle draw, but their celebration is short-lived. Chaos ensues as people attempt to take the car, and they are forced to navigate unexpected events.

Home.name: The Guardians of the Galaxy Holiday Special
Home.description: The Guardians are on a mission to make Christmas unforgettable for Quill and head to Earth in search of the perfect present.

Home.name: Operation Fortune: Ruse de Guerre
Home.description: Elite spy Orson Fortune must track down and stop the sale of a deadly new weapons technology wielded by billionaire arms broker Greg Simmonds. Reluctantly teamed up with some of the world's best operatives, Fortune and his crew recruit Hollywood's biggest movie star, Danny Francesco, to help them on their globe-trotting mission to save the world.

Home.name: Guess Who's Coming to Dinner
Home.description: Joanna, a young woman raised with liberal values, brings home her fiance John, a widowed, black physician. Over dinner, Joanna's parents' apprehensions become evident causing trouble for the couple.

Home.name: R.I.P.D. 2: Rise of the Damned
Home.description: Recruited by the R.I.P.D., a resurrected sheriff returns to Earth to save humanity from a gateway to hell.

Home.name: Janhit Mein Jaari
Home.description: With the will to break taboo as her armour of choice, Mannu embarks to work as a condom salesperson, despite the reservations of her family and society.

Home.name: Easy A
Home.description: When Olive lies to her best friend about losing her virginity to one of the college boys, a girl overhears their conversation. Soon, her story spreads across the entire school like wildfire.

Home.name: Lady Bird
Home.description: As senior year comes to an end, Lady Bird must strive to navigate through the ups and downs in her relationships while trying to get into a prestigious college and become popular.

Home.name: Mrs Undercover
Home.description: Mrs Undercover is a 2023 Indian Hindi-language spy comedy movie directed by Anushree Mehta and produced by Abir Sengupta, Anushree Mehta, Varun Bajaj, Ishan Saksena and Sunil Shah. The film stars are Radhika Apte, Sumeet Vyas and Rajesh Sharma in key roles. The film premiered on 14 April 2023 on ZEE5.

Home.name: Andaz Apna Apna
Home.description: Amar and Prem, who belong to middle-class families, compete to win over Raveena, a millionaire's daughter. Along the way, they run into a local gangster, Teja, who turns their lives upside down.

Home.name: The Nice Guys
Home.description: Amelia, a girl in hiding, hires Healy to put March, a detective seeking her, in his place. After two hitmen try to get Healy to reveal her whereabouts, he concernedly pairs with March to find her.

Home.name: Detective Chinatown 3
Home.description: Baiqiang Wang and Haoran Liu are back solving mysteries and fighting crime in the third entry in the hugely successful Chinese buddy action-comedy series.

Home.name: Millionaires Express
Home.description: A man returns to his hometown and sabotages a train so that the millionaires on board will spend money in town.

Home.name: Gol Maal
Home.description: Ramprasad works for Bhavani, who discourages his employees from pursuing any hobbies. Things take a hilarious turn when Bhavani catches Ramprasad at a hockey match and he lies about having a twin.

Home.name: Kanjoos Makhichoos
Home.description: Kanjoos Makhichoos is a 2023 Indian Hindi-language comedy film directed by Vipul Mehta and produced by Soham Rockstar Entertainment along with ThunderSky Entertainment. The film is based on the famous Gujarati play Sajan Re Jhooth Mat Bolo.

Home.name: Stuart Little 2
Home.description: George must cover for Stuart at home while he and Snowbell set out across the city in search of his new friend Margalo, a canary. Stuart faces many obstacles during his mission to rescue Margalo.

Home.name: Yes Man
Home.description: Carl, a lonely man with low self-esteem, participates in a self-help programme that challenges him to say yes to everything in life for an entire year.

Home.name: The Names of Love
Home.description: In her attempts to convert her political opponents, provocative activist Bahia openly flirts and sleeps with those who don't agree with her until they change their mind. However, everything changes when she meets an uptight scientist.

Home.name: Night Shift
Home.description: Chuck (Henry Winkler) has given up life as a stockbroker because it was too stressful. Now, he works an easy gig as a night shift attendant at a New York City morgue. His co-worker, Bill Blazejowski (Michael Keaton), on the other hand, is always looking to make a quick buck. When Bill finds out that Chuck's prostitute neighbor, Belinda (Shelley Long), needs a place to do her work, he convinces Chuck to turn the morgue into a brothel where they can work as her pimps.

Home.name: On a Magical Night
Home.description: After 20 years of marriage, Maria decides to leave her home, go to the hotel across the street and contemplate her life.

Home.name: Kung Fu Panda 2
Home.description: Dragon Warrior Po takes it upon himself to foil the plans of murderous peacock Shen who intends to conquer China and destroy kung fu. For this, Po has to unveil the mystery of his own past.

Home.name: The Nutty Professor
Home.description: Sherman, an extremely overweight genetics professor, falls in love with a colleague. But when he experiments on himself with a slimming potion, it not only trims him down but also makes him obnoxious.

Home.name: Kidon
Home.description: On the 18th of February 2010 in Tel Aviv, the world discovers in the papers pictures of the Mossad agents caught while killing Mahmoud ai Mabhouh in Dubain a month earlier. It was the first time Israeli agents were caught on simple security cameras.

Home.name: Kickboxer
Home.description: Kurt decides to go in search of a kung fu master when his brother, Eric, is paralysed during a fight. While training himself to avenge Eric's defeat, he finds himself trapped in a criminal intrigue.

Home.name: Bachchhan Paandey
Home.description: To succeed in the film industry, Myra chooses Bachchhan Paandey, a notorious hooligan, as the main focus of her new movie. Things get complicated when the gangster decides to act in the film.

Home.name: A Man Called Otto
Home.description: When a lively young family moves in next door, grumpy widower Otto Anderson meets his match in a quick-witted, pregnant woman named Marisol, leading to an unlikely friendship that turns his world upside down.

Home.description: Jaggu Ani Juliet is a 2023 Indian Marathi-language Romantic Comedy film directed by Mahesh Limaye. It is produced by Punit Balan Studios.
