Home.name: Middle Class Love
Home.description: Unhappy with his family's middle-class lifestyle, young Yudi assumes that joining a renowned college and having a wealthy girlfriend are the best ways to escape it.

Home.name: Tu Jhoothi Main Makkaar
Home.description: Tu Jhoothi Main Makkaar, also abbreviated as TJMM, is a 2023 Indian Hindi-language romantic comedy film directed by Luv Ranjan and written by Rahul Mody, Luv Ranjan.

Home.name: Swept Away
Home.description: A haughty rich housewife and her shipmate get stranded in a thunderstorm. Suddenly, the rules governing their relationship change when she has to depend on her shipmate for survival.

Home.name: Happy Feet Two
Home.description: When the penguins face a new threat, Mumble, with the help of his family and friends, decides to bring together the entire penguin population in order to save their species.

Home.name: Nautanki Saala!
Home.description: Ram, a successful theatre artist, saves Mandar from committing suicide. He then ends up developing a special bond with Mandar and even helps solve his problems.

Home.name: Selfiee
Home.description: Bollywood superstar Vijay Kumar needs to get a new driver's license from an RTO officer. However, a misunderstanding leads to a war of words between the two, eventually escalating into a feud which is played out in front of the entire country.

Home.name: Arthur Newman
Home.description: After years of leading a dreary life filled with regret, a former pro golfer, Wallace Avery, decides to fake his death and start his life afresh as Arthur Newman.

Home.name: Ninnila Ninnila
Home.description: Dev, a cook, meets Tara, a young woman, and soon love blossoms between them. However, he is unable to let go of his past, which haunts him in the form of hallucinations.

Home.name: The Man from Toronto (Hindi)
Home.description: A case of mistaken identity forces a bumbling entrepreneur to team up with a notorious assassin in hopes of staying alive.

Home.name: Baadshah
Home.description: Raj, a small-time private detective who is desperate for a big break, gets drawn into a political conspiracy when he is hired to rescue a hostage.

Home.name: Police Story
Home.description: Hong Kong policeman Kevin single-handedly arrests a notorious drug lord. But, he is soon framed for murdering another policeman and must clear his name before it's too late.

Home.name: Jennifer's Body
Home.description: Jennifer becomes possessed and turns into a succubus after she is sacrificed to Satan. When her best friend Anita learns about it, she has to stop Jennifer before she attacks her lover Chip.

Home.name: Your Place or Mine
Home.description: Debbie and Peter are best friends and total opposites. She craves routine with her son in LA, but he thrives on change in NY. When they swap houses and lives for a week they discover what they think they want might not be what they really need.

Home.name: Mukundan Unni Associates
Home.description: Lawyer Mukundan Unni has dreams of becoming successful and attempts to achieve growth, prosperity, and respect.

Home.name: Puss in Boots: The Last Wish
Home.description: Puss in Boots discovers that his passion for adventure has taken its toll: he has burnt through eight of his nine lives. Puss sets out on an epic journey to find the mythical Last Wish and restore his nine lives.

Home.name: Kuttey
Home.description: One rainy night in the outskirts of Mumbai, three stray gangs unknowingly cross paths on the hunt and it's every man for himself.

Home.name: White Noise
Home.description: College professor Jack Gladney and his family's comfortable suburban life is upended when a nearby chemical leak causes "The Airborne Toxic Event," releasing a noxious black cloud over the region that forces the Gladney family to evacuate.

Home.name: Amsterdam
Home.description: Set in the '30s, it follows three friends who witness a murder, become suspects themselves, and uncover one of the most outrageous plots in American history.

Home.name: Cirkus
Home.description: After finding two sets of identical twins on the doorstep of his orphanage, Dr. Roy Jamnadas gives them up for adoption to two different families in two different cities. Years later, a comedy of errors ensues when one set of twins decides to visit the city where the other set of twins runs a circus.

Home.name: Govinda Naam Mera
Home.description: With an abusive wife, a girlfriend and a court case, Govinda Waghmare is not able to catch a break. The icing on top of that cake is murder.

Home.name: Bhediya
Home.description: Bhaskar finds himself changing after being bitten by a wolf in the forests of Arunachal. While Bhaskar begins to transform into a shape-shifting werewolf, he and his friends look for answers amid many twists, turns and laughs.

Home.name: Monica, O My Darling
Home.description: A young man desperately tries to make it big with some unlikely allies and a dastardly diabolical plan to pull off the perfect murder.

Home.name: Tadka
Home.description: Tadka is an Indian Hindi-language romantic comedy-drama film directed by actor Prakash Raj, starring Nana Patekar, Ali Fazal, Shriya Saran and Tapsee Pannu. The story of the film is based in Goa and filming began in May 2016. It is a remake of the 2011 Malayalam film Salt N' Pepper.

Home.name: Double XL
Home.description: Two plus size women, one from the heartland of Uttar Pradesh and the other from urban New Delhi, discover themselves as they navigate life, celebrate female friendship and embrace body positivity, breaking the myth that beauty corresponds to size.

Home.name: Lyle, Lyle, Crocodile
Home.description: When the Primm family moves to New York City, their young son, Josh, struggles to adapt to his new school and friends. All of that changes when he discovers Lyle, a singing crocodile that loves baths, caviar and great music. The two become fast friends, but when evil neighbor Mr. Grumps threatens Lyle's existence, the Primms must band together to show the world that family can come from the most unexpected places.

Home.name: Paws of Fury: The Legend of Hank
Home.description: A down-on-his-luck hound finds himself in a town full of cats who need a hero to defend them from a ruthless villain's evil plot to wipe their village off the map. With help from a reluctant trainer, the underdog must assume the role of fearsome samurai and team up with the felines to save the day. The only problem is -- they all hate dogs.

Home.name: Thank God
Home.description: A real estate broker meets with an accident and wakes up in heaven, only to be informed by God that he must play a "Game of Life." If he manages to win, he'll be sent back to Earth, but he'll be sent to hell if he loses.

Home.name: The Man from Toronto
Home.description: A case of mistaken identity forces a bumbling entrepreneur to team up with a notorious assassin in hopes of staying alive.

Home.name: The Unbearable Weight of Massive Talent
Home.description: Unfulfilled and facing financial ruin, actor Nick Cage accepts a $1 million offer to attend a wealthy fan's birthday party. Things take a wildly unexpected turn when a CIA operative recruits Cage for an unusual mission. Taking on the role of a lifetime, he soon finds himself channeling his most iconic and beloved characters to save himself and his loved ones.

Home.name: Atithi Bhooto Bhava
Home.description: Atithi Bhooto Bhava is an Indian Hindi-language horror comedy film written by Aniket Wakchaure and directed by Hardik Gajjar. It features Jackie Shroff, Pratik Gandhi and Sharmin Segal in lead roles. The film went on floors in January 2021. It was released on ZEE5 on September 23, 2022.

Home.name: Bullet Train
Home.description: Ladybug is an unlucky assassin who's determined to do his job peacefully after one too many gigs has gone off the rails. Fate, however, may have other plans as his latest mission puts him on a collision course with lethal adversaries from around the globe -- all with connected yet conflicting objectives -- on the world's fastest train.

Home.name: The Rundown
Home.description: Beck, a bounty hunter, visits the Amazon jungle to bring home his boss's son, Travis. Soon, they find themselves in danger as local goons wish to acquire the priceless artefact in their possession.

Home.name: Vellimoonga
Home.description: A middle-aged politician falls in love with a girl half his age, only to discover later that she is the daughter of the woman who he loved in his childhood.

Home.name: Big Fat Liar
Home.description: Jason Shephard writes a story that falls into the hands of a Hollywood producer, Marty Wolf. When Marty turns it into a blockbuster movie and takes the credit, Jason vows to make him confess.

Home.name: Jaadugar
Home.description: A small-time magician with no athletic talent must compete in a football tournament to win the heart of the woman he loves.

Home.name: Private Lessons
Home.description: Teenager Phillip Fillmore (Eric Brown) is out of school for the summer, his millionaire father is out of town on business, and he's got the mansion to himself, with the sexy Dutch maid Nicole (Sylvia Kristel) to keep him company. It sounds like a dream summer, until Nicole starts acting strangely familiar toward Phillip, who isn't quite sure how to react. Meanwhile, chauffeur Lester (Howard Hesseman) seems to have something up his sleeve as well, which doesn't bode well for poor Phillip.

Home.name: Ron's Gone Wrong
Home.description: Barney is a socially awkward schoolboy who receives a robot named Ron -- a walking, talking, digitally connected device that's supposed to be his best friend. Barney is excited to finally have his own robot -- until his new toy starts to hilariously malfunction, drawing the attention of a shady executive who wants to protect his company's stock price at all costs.

Home.name: Varudu Kaavalenu
Home.description: Bhoomi, the owner of an eco-friendly start-up business in Hyderabad, is reluctant to get married. However, this begins to change when she meets Aakash, a successful architect.

Home.name: Hunterrr
Home.description: Mandar is a self-confessed sex addict who is only interested in sex and holds no regards for love or feelings. However, his life changes when he meets Tripti and wishes to settle down with her.

Home.name: Dead in a Week: Or Your Money Back
Home.description: A depressed writer hires an assassin to kill him after he fails to commit suicide. However, the writer falls in love and starts having second thoughts about his decision.

Home.name: Something New
Home.description: Pursuing a career has made Kenya's life dull, or so believe her friends who set her up for a blind date. But when Brian turns out to be white, Kenya backs off, not knowing that cupid will strike soon.

Home.name: The Squid And The Whale
Home.description: Although the Berkman family appears to be an ideal one, they live a disjointed life. When the parents get separated, the children must deal with the trauma.

Home.name: The Sea Beast
Home.description: The life of a legendary sea monster hunter is turned upside down when a young girl stows away on his ship.

Home.name: Minions: The Rise of Gru
Home.description: In the 1970s, young Gru tries to join a group of supervillains called the Vicious 6 after they oust their leader -- the legendary fighter Wild Knuckles. When the interview turns disastrous, Gru and his Minions go on the run with the Vicious 6 hot on their tails. Luckily, he finds an unlikely source for guidance -- Wild Knuckles himself -- and soon discovers that even bad guys need a little help from their friends.

Home.name: Lover
Home.description: Charitha, a doctor, endangers her life when she saves a child from being kidnapped for her liver. Later, Raj, who is in love with Charitha, protects her when goons try to kill her.

Home.name: Middle School: The Worst Years of My Life
Home.description: Rafe plans to break all uncompromising policies enacted by his school as he thinks the rules prevent students from expressing themselves.

Home.name: Saunkan Saunkne
Home.description: Married for many years, Nirmal and Naseeb have lost all hope of having a child. Naseeb persuades Nirmal to marry her younger sister, but sharing her husband proves more difficult than she thought.

Home.name: Over Her Dead Body
Home.description: Kate turns into a ghost after she dies on the day of her wedding. She then decides to sabotage her ex-fiance's new relationship with a psychic.

Home.name: Suraj Pe Mangal Bhari
Home.description: Suraj, an eligible bachelor, finds himself getting rejected by the families of many potential brides. Soon, he learns that a wedding detective named Madhu Mangal Rane is the reason.

Home.name: Fighting with My Family
Home.description: Paige and Zak are children of wrestlers who dream of entering the same profession as their parents. However, only Paige gets the opportunity and she has to learn how to face the world on her own.

Home.name: Chandni Chowk to China
Home.description: Sidhu's friend tricks him into believing that he's the reincarnation of a slain Chinese revolutionary. Sidhu visits China to save his people but faces challenges, including a deadly female assassin.

Home.name: Chal Mera Putt 2
Home.description: A tale of everlasting love between illegal immigrants struggling for their permanent residency in the UK. The pair face challenges and struggles together and learn to overcome them.

Home.name: Axone
Home.description: Friends from Northeast India prepare a pungent delicacy for a wedding celebration, sparking conflict and comedy with their unaccustomed new neighbours in Delhi.

Home.name: Besharam
Home.description: Babli is a small-time thief who steals cars in order to support a noble cause. His life takes an interesting turn when he falls in love with Tara and decides to mend his ways.

Home.name: Badhaai Ho
Home.description: Nakul, a 25-year-old man, is shocked to discover that his mother is pregnant. His struggle to come to terms with the news puts his relationship with his girlfriend, Renee, in jeopardy.

Home.name: 100% Wolf
Home.description: Freddy Lupin comes from a proud family line of werewolves. Positive he'll become the most fearsome werewolf ever, Freddy is in for a shock when his first warfing goes awry, turning him into a ferocious poodle.

Home.name: Good Newwz
Home.description: Two married couples are unsuccessful in conceiving and seek medical treatment. However, they end up in a complicated situation after their doctor makes a blunder.

Home.name: Bhool Bhulaiyaa
Home.description: An NRI and his wife decide to stay in his ancestral home, paying no heed to the warnings about ghosts. Soon, inexplicable occurrences cause him to call a psychiatrist to help solve the mystery.

Home.name: Super Nani
Home.description: Mann's grandmother Bharti is scorned and ill-treated by her family. To make them realise her worth, Mann gives her a complete makeover and also convinces her to take up modelling opportunities.

Home.name: Tanu Weds Manu Returns
Home.description: After Tanu and Manu's marriage falls apart, the latter finds himself smitten by Datto, a lookalike of his ex-wife. But soon enough, the estranged couple's feelings begin to spark again.

Home.name: Honey, I Shrunk the Kids
Home.description: A scientist tries his best to get his recent invention, a shrinking machine, to work. Things go awry when he accidentally shrinks his children and throws them along with the garbage.

Home.name: Sardar Ka Grandson
Home.description: When Amreek discovers that his grandmother, Sardar Kaur, is ill, he immediately comes home from Los Angeles. He then tries to help her reunite with her old home.

Home.name: Bareilly Ki Barfi
Home.description: After reading a book that changes her life, Bitti is intent on meeting the author. Her quest takes her to a publisher, Chirag, who leads her to believe that the writer is Pritam Vidrohi.

Home.name: Total Dhamaal
Home.description: When a plane carrying a thief's treasure crashes in Janakpur, a group of eccentric people and seasoned con artists compete against each other to find it first.

Home.name: Stree
Home.description: The people of Chanderi live under constant fear of Stree, the spirit of a woman who attacks men at night during festivals. Vicky, along with his friends, decides to unravel the mystery.

Home.name: The DUFF
Home.description: When Bianca realises that she is being used by people to get to her popular friends, she decides to change. She begs her former friend to rebuild her image in exchange for teaching him science.

Home.name: Garam Masala
Home.description: Shyam and Makarand, two photographer friends, like to flirt with women constantly. After a trip abroad, Shyam decides to disrupt Makarand's life when he sees him enjoying the company of three ladies.

Home.name: Neighbors
Home.description: Mac and Kelly's peaceful suburban life is offset by a fraternity house next door, which is inhabited by constantly partying college students who refuse to be quiet no matter how hard the couple try.

Home.name: Judgementall Hai Kya
Home.description: Bobby, a dubbing artist who is haunted by a childhood trauma, rents out a portion of her house to Keshav and Rima. However, she repeatedly stalks the young couple and is suspicious of Keshav.

Home.name: Ice Age: The Meltdown
Home.description: Manny, Sid and Diego discover that the ice dam protecting the valley they were residing in was about to fall and eventually lead to floods. Soon after, they scamper off to find a safer habitat.

Home.name: Door Ke Darshan
Home.description: When the matriarch of a dysfunctional family wakes up after a 30-year-long coma, the meMBers of the household set aside their differences to help her adapt to the changes in her life.

Home.name: Kung Fu Panda
Home.description: When Po the Panda, a kung fu enthusiast, gets selected as the Dragon Warrior, he decides to team up with the Furious Five and destroy the evil forces that threaten the Valley of Peace.

Home.name: Ted
Home.description: A wish comes true for John when his teddy bear, Ted, comes to life. When he plans to move in with his girlfriend, Ted, who is not prepared for the change, unintentionally ruins their relationship.

Home.name: Housefull 4
Home.description: Three brothers are set to marry three sisters. However, a peek into the distant past reveals to one of the brothers that their brides have been mixed up in their current reincarnation.

Home.name: Rough Night
Home.description: Jess and her four friends reunite after ten years to celebrate her impending wedding. However, things take an unexpected turn when the girls accidentally kill the male stripper that they had hired.

Home.name: Chhalaang
Home.description: Montu is a lazy physical training instructor who does the bare minimum to stay employed. However, a new teacher threatens to take his job and the woman he loves.

Home.name: Rangeela Raja
Home.description: Rangeela Raja is a 2019 Indian Hindi-language comedy-drama film directed by Sikander Bharti and written and produced by Pahlaj Nihalani. Starring Govinda, Mishika Chourasia and Anupama Agnihotri, the film was released on 18 January 2019. The film is a remake of Netrikan.

Home.name: Badnaam Gali
Home.description: Badnaam Gali is 2019 Indian Hindi film released on ZEE5 on 10 May 2019. The film is about a surrogate mother. The film stars Patralekha Paul and Divyendu Sharma. The web film released on the occasion of Mother's Day. The film deals with surrogacy in a humorous way.

Home.name: Red Notice
Home.description: In the world of international crime, an Interpol agent attempts to hunt down and capture the world's most wanted art thief.

Home.name: Piranha 3DD
Home.description: Piranha 3D is a 2010 American comedy-horror film that serves as a loose remake of the comedy horror film Piranha (1978) and an entry in the Piranha film series. During spring break on Lake Victoria, a popular waterside resort, an underground tremor releases hundreds of prehistoric, carnivorous piranhas into the lake.

Home.name: Tiki Taka
Home.description: Khelechi, an African native, visits West Bengal to meet a gangster and befriends Raju, a cab driver. Hilarity ensues when Raju touts Khelechi as a great footballer and he gains popularity overnight.

Home.name: Maska
Home.description: Determined to make it in Bollywood, an aspiring actor considers turning his back on his family's caf business.

Home.name: Santhu Straight Forward (Hindi)
Home.description: Santhu, a middle-class man, falls in love with Ananya, an architecture student. However, he realises that she is engaged to Dev, a gangster, and strives to win her over.

Home.name: 17 Again
Home.description: Mike is unhappy with the way his life has turned out and wishes he could be 17 again to change it. One day, he wakes up to find that his wish has been granted.

Home.name: Encanto
Home.description: The Madrigals are an extraordinary family who live hidden in the mountains of ColoMBia in a charmed place called the Encanto. The magic of the Encanto has blessed every child in the family with a unique gift -- every child except Mirabel. However, she soon may be the Madrigals last hope when she dis

Home.name: Jhootha Kahin Ka
Home.description: Karan and Varun go to Mauritius to study but decide to stay back as they enjoy their new lifestyle. However, things take an unusual turn when their parents come to stay with them.

Home.name: Fifty Shades of Black
Home.description: In a spoof of "Fifty Shades of Grey," Hannah Steele interviews entrepreneur Christian Black (Marlon Wayans) for her roommate's school newspaper. The wealthy and eligible Black quickly learns how clumsy the young woman is. As flirtation leads to attraction, Christian invites Hannah to his home and introduces her to his kinky world of S&M. Despite their different backgrounds, the new couple consistently surprise each other with how far they're willing to go to make their relationship work.

Home.name: Hum Do Hamare Do
Home.description: Hum Do Hamare Do is a 2021 Indian Hindi-language comedy drama film directed by Abhishek Jain and produced by Dinesh Vijan. The film features Rajkummar Rao, Kriti Sanon, Paresh Rawal and Ratna Pathak Shah in the lead roles. Aparshakti Khurana, Manu Rishi and Prachi Shah feature in supporting roles.

Home.name: Happy Bhag Jayegi
Home.description: Happy, a vibrant Indian girl, elopes on the day of her wedding so that she can marry Guddu, the man she loves. She mistakenly arrives at the home of a Pakistani politician where chaos ensues.

Home.name: Super
Home.description: An ordinary man who has lived a disappointing life decides to transform himself into a superhero and fight crime when his wife, a recovering addict, leaves him for another man.

Home.name: The Boss Baby: Family Business
Home.description: When a vicious professor attempts to destroy childhoods, the Boss Baby sets out on a mission to put a stop to his plans.

Home.name: Jurmana (Radha)
Home.description: Police officer Radha Krishna is transferred to Hyderabad, where a boMB goes off at politician Sujatha's election campaign. Radha vows to take revenge, only to discover that all is not what it seems.

Home.name: The Parent Trap
Home.description: Identical twins Hallie and Annie are separated after their parents' divorce. Years later, they discover each other at a summer camp and decide to switch places in an effort to reunite their parents.

Home.name: The Babysitter: Killer Queen
Home.description: Two years after defeating a satanic cult led by his babysitter Bee, Cole once again has to outsmart the forces of evil when old enemies unexpectedly return.

Home.name: Lootcase
Home.description: Nandan, a middle-class man, finds a suitcase full of money near his workplace and steals it. However, he is soon chased by a police officer, a notorious gangster and a corrupt politician.

Home.name: Munna Bhai M.B.B.S.
Home.description: Munna is a goon who sets out to fulfil his father's dream of becoming a doctor. With some help from his ally, Circuit, he enrols himself in a medical college and drives Dr Asthana up the wall.

Home.name: Boo 2! A Madea Halloween
Home.description: Madea, Bam, and Hattie find themselves in trouble when they encounter monsters, goblins and boogeyman at a haunted campsite.

Home.name: Chup Chup Ke
Home.description: A fisherman saves Jeetu from committing suicide, only to sell him to a moneylender. Jeetu is then forced to pose as a man with hearing and speech impairment, resulting in hilarious consequences.

Home.name: Sing 2
Home.description: Can-do koala Buster Moon and his all-star cast of animal performers prepare to launch a dazzling stage extravaganza in the glittering entertainment capital of the world. There's just one hitch -- he has to find and persuade the world's most reclusive rock star to join them. What begins as Buster's d

Home.name: Motichoor Chaknachoor
Home.description: Anita whose single purpose in life is to marry a foreign-settled groom decides to marry Pushpinder, a 36-year-old Dubai-returned professional, who is desperate for a bride.

Home.name: Diary of a Wimpy Kid
Home.description: Greg Heffley dreams of becoming famous while surviving middle school with his best friend, Rowley.

Home.name: Bunty Aur Babli 2
Home.description: Bunty and Babli are a pair of retired con-artists. After a spate of robberies with their trademark sigil start appearing across India the two are forced out of retirement to find out who has been copying them.

Home.name: Arjun Patiala
Home.description: Arjun, a police officer, attempts to rid his town of crime with the help of his confidant, Onida Singh. While at it, he falls in love with Ritu, a news reporter with an agenda of her own.

Home.name: Kaale Dhande
Home.description: Kaale Dhande is a ZEE5 Marathi Original comedy series starring Mahesh Manjrekar, Shubhankar Tawade, Neha Khan, Onkar Raut and Nikhil Ratnaparkhi. This bold, new age laugh riot revolves around Vicky, a young photographer, whose life turns upside down due to various unforeseen situations.

Home.name: Ghostbusters: Afterlife
Home.description: When a single mother and her two children move to a new town, they soon discover they have a connection to the original Ghostbusters and the secret legacy their grandfather left behind.

Home.name: Khiladi 786
Home.description: Mansukh's father runs a marriage bureau and believes that his son is a failure in life. In order to prove him wrong, Mansukh takes on the task of finding a match for a gangster's sister.

Home.name: Bombairiya
Home.description: All hell breaks loose when Meghna, a PR agent's phone gets stolen. A stranger named Abhishek decides to help her and the duo gets eMBroiled in chaotic situations, unaware of what is to follow.

Home.name: Shimla Mirchi
Home.description: While on a family trip to Shimla, Avinash falls in love with Naina who stays with her mother. However, things get complicated when Naina gives Avinash's love letter to her mother.

Home.name: Sister Act
Home.description: Deloris, a lounge singer, is persuaded to go into witness protection as a nun at a convent after she witnesses a murder. But once there, she has trouble adjusting to her new lifestyle.

Home.name: Sholay
Home.description: Jai and Veeru, two ex-convicts, are hired by Thakur Baldev Singh, a retired policeman, to help him nab Gabbar Singh, a notorious dacoit, who has spread havoc in the village of Ramgarh.

Home.name: Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle
Home.description: When four students play with a magical video game, they are drawn to the jungle world of Jumanji, where they are trapped as their avatars. To return to the real world, they must finish the game.

Home.name: Gulabo Sitabo
Home.description: Mirza, an old man, is always at war with his tenant Baankey as he wants him to evict his house but Baankey is hell-bent on staying.

Home.name: Khandaani Shafakhana
Home.description: Babita Bedi, a medical representative and the sole breadwinner of the family, is asked to run a fertility clinic for six months. She must be able to sell it or she may lose everything.

Home.name: The Boss Baby
Home.description: Seven-year-old Tim gets jealous when his parents give all their attention to his little brother. Tim soon learns that the baby can talk and the two team up to foil the plans of the CEO of Puppy Co.

Home.name: Beats
Home.description: A reclusive, teenage music prodigy forms an unlikely friendship with a struggling producer. United by their mutual love of hip-hop, they try to free each other from the demons of their past and break into the city's music scene.

Home.name: The Witches
Home.description: When an orphan encounters a witch, his grandmother takes him to a hotel in order to protect him. But in the same hotel, a group of witches is plotting to get rid of the children of the world.

Home.name: The Way of the Househusband
Home.description: Tatsu, a once-legendary yakuza known as the Immortal Dragon, gives up a life of crime to become a stay-at-home husband.

Home.name: 3 Idiots
Home.description: In college, Farhan and Raju form a great bond with Rancho due to his refreshing outlook. Years later, a bet gives them a chance to look for their long-lost friend whose existence seems rather elusive.

Home.name: FALLBACK
Home.description: Michelle (Rhian Ramos) is not one to let herself get hurt in love. With this fear, she thrusts herself in the midst of plan Bs, second options, and back-up plans - one which involves her present boyfriend (Daniel Matsunaga) and her ex (Zanjoe Marudo).

Home.name: Golmaal Again
Home.description: Five orphan men return to the orphanage they grew up in to attend their mentor's funeral. However, they encounter the ghost of their childhood friend, Khushi, and help her attain salvation.

Home.name: Kala Shah Kala
Home.description: Lovely, a dark-complexioned man, gets married to Pammi, a beautiful girl. However, his bliss is short-lived as Pammi appears to be possessed by a spirit.

Home.name: Ujda Chaman
Home.description: Chaman, a lecturer, has trouble finding a suitable bride due to his receding hairline. All hell breaks loose when an astrologer predicts that he will remain celibate if unmarried till the age of 31.

Home.name: Roohi
Home.description: Bhawra and Kattanni kidnap Roohi on the orders of Guniya Bhai, who wants to marry her off to his client. However, things take a paranormal turn when they realise that Roohi is possessed by a demon.

Home.name: Laxmii
Home.description: Aasif visits his wife's parents' house and happens to go to a ground that is supposedly haunted. However, he is soon possessed by the spirit of a transgender who is out for revenge.

Home.name: Jai Mummy Di
Home.description: A lovestruck couple decides to take their relationship to the next level and get married. However, they hit a bumpy road when they learn that their mothers do not like each other.

Home.name: Made in China
Home.description: Raghu, a failing entrepreneur, travels to China in search of new business opportunities. However, chaos ensues when he tries to capitalise on a dubious aphrodisiac.

Home.name: Paani Ch Madhaani
Home.description: A group of musicians travel to London after finding renewed success with a new singer. They end up winning the lottery, but misplace the winning ticket.

Home.name: American Wedding
Home.description: It's the wedding of Jim and Michelle and the gathering of their families and friends, including Jim's old friends from high school and Michelle's little sister. Cast: Jason Biggs, Alyson Hannigan.

Home.name: Regular Show: The Movie
Home.description: Mordecai and RiGBy, a talking blue jay and a raccoon, must defeat a wicked volleyball coach to save the world.

Home.name: Rocket Singh: Salesman of the Year
Home.description: Harpreet Singh Bedi, a commerce graduate, becomes a salesman. After being ridiculed by his colleagues and his employer, he plans to operate a parallel company without their knowledge.

Home.name: The Cowboy Way
Home.description: Comedy about two friends and rodeo partners who travel to New York to find their missing friend and his daughter. The search for the missing duo, paves way for a wacky adventure.

Home.name: Sonic the Hedgehog
Home.description: An extraterrestrial hedgehog is discovered by a scientist with evil intentions and plans to use his superpowers for his selfish needs.

Home.name: Home Sweet Home Alone
Home.description: A married couple tries to steal back a valuable heirloom from a troublesome kid.

Home.name: Dirty Grandpa
Home.description: After his wife's demise, Dick tricks his grandson, Jason, to drive him to Florida. Unaware of Dick's intentions, Jason finds himself in a series of misadventures.

Home.name: Grown Ups
Home.description: Five childhood friends take their families for a weekend trip to a lake house in their hometown, where they reunite to attend the funeral of their former high school basketball coach.

Home.name: Kung Fu Hustle
Home.description: An aspiring gangster pretends to be part of a notorious gang and tries to terrorise a neighbourhood. However, unknown to him, three martial arts experts live there and are ready to take him down.

Home.name: Sarileru Neekevvaru
Home.description: Ajay, an army major, journeys to Kurnool when he is assigned a covert mission. However, he finds himself in the middle of a major scam and sets out to uncover the truth.

Home.name: Grown Ups 2
Home.description: Lenny Feder moves his family to his hometown and looks forward to spending time with his old friends. However, he and his companions soon face bizarre situations and new enemies.

Home.name: Sonu Ke Titu Ki Sweety
Home.description: Childhood friends Sonu and Titu's friendship is tested when an innocent Titu decides to marry Sweety, who is not just behind his money but is hell-bent on breaking their friendship too.

Home.name: Chhello Divas
Home.description: Eight young friends experience a series of adventures and misadventures as they make their gradual transition to adulthood in their last year of college.

Home.name: All Is Well
Home.description: Inder, a musician, returns to India to find out that his father owes money to a local goon, Cheema. They run away to avoid Cheema but mend their own dysfunctional bonds on the way.

Home.name: Meet the Spartans
Home.description: Leonidas, a young Spartan warrior, takes a handful of warriors along with him on a mission to bring down an evil, overweight Persian ruler, Xerxes.

Home.name: OMG: Oh My God!
Home.description: When an earthquake destroys an atheist Kanji's antique shop, he decides to sue God. However, when Lord Krishna helps him fight the lawsuit and expose the corrupt charlatans, his faith is restored.

Home.name: Arctic Dogs
Home.description: Swifty the fox discovers a devious plan by Otto Von Walrus to drill beneath the Arctic surface to unleash enough gas to melt all the ice. With help from his friends -- an introverted polar bear, a scatterbrained albatross, a crafty fox and two paranoid otters -- Swifty and the gang spring into action to foil Otto's plot and save the day.

Home.name: Dolphin Reef
Home.description: Echo, a young Pacific bottlenose dolphin, seems more interested in exploring his coral reef home and its inhabitants than learning to survive in it, but lessons from his family may encourage Echo to master his vital role in the marine community.

Home.name: Spies in Disguise
Home.description: Lance Sterling, a secret agent, finds himself transformed into a pigeon. He then sets out with his associate Walter to stop a villain who is using Sterling's disguise to carry out a dangerous plan.

Home.name: Toy Story 4
Home.description: Woody attempts to make Forky, a toy, suffering from existential crisis, realise his importance in the life of Bonnie, their owner. However, things become difficult when Gabby Gabby enters their lives.

Home.name: Thana Sadar
Home.description: A fearless police officer makes a foolproof plan to capture an international criminal. However, things take a dramatic turn when the criminal learns about certain events at the police department.

Home.name: Hasee Toh Phasee
Home.description: Nikhil is a struggling businessman who thinks he is in love with his girlfriend, Karishma, and wants to marry her. But he ends up falling in love with her smart, geeky and quirky sister, Meeta.

Home.name: Khosla Ka Ghosla
Home.description: Kamal Khosla's land is grabbed by a thug named Khurana. In a bid to retrieve their land, Khosla's son Cherry and his friends step in armed with a clever plan to fool the crook.

Home.name: Housefull 2
Home.description: Four men join hands to date and marry the women of their dreams by changing their identities and deceiving their prospective fathers-in-law.

Home.name: Badmaash Company
Home.description: Karan, a young middle-class graduate, is devastated when his mother sells her jewellery to fund his father's hospitalisation. Vowing to remedy the situation, he devises a plan to become rich quickly.

Home.name: Minions
Home.description: Minions Kevin, Stuart and Bob decide to find a new master. They eMBark on a global trip and meet Scarlett Overkill, a female super-villain who recruits them and hatches a plan to take over the world.

Home.name: George of the Jungle
Home.description: Baby George is the lone survivor of a plane crash and is raised by a wise gorilla in the jungle. One day, he saves Ursula and moves from his sweet jungle life in Africa to San Francisco.

Home.name: Vampire Dog
Home.description: 12-year-old Ace inherits Fang, a dog that turns out to be a 600-year-old talking vampire dog with unusual abilities, and together they set out on an adventure.

Home.name: Dumb And Dumber To
Home.description: Long-time friends and colossal fools Harry and Lloyd eMBark on a journey to find Harry's newly-discovered daughter and convince her to donate a kidney to Harry, whose health is deteriorating.

Home.name: Deya Neya
Home.description: Prasanta, the son of a wealthy businessman, aspires to become a famous singer. However, when he leaves for Kolkata to fulfil his dreams, he falls in love with Sucharita.

Home.name: Dhilluku Dhuddu
Home.description: Kumar and Kajal are in love but her father is against the match and tries to have Kumar killed with the help of Mani. Things go awry when Mani invites Kumar's family to a haunted house.

Home.name: 18 Fatal Strikes
Home.description: After an Abbot Monk is injured and taken into the home of two young men, the men find themselves targets of the Ching Army and its evil leader: Wong Wu Ti.

Home.name: Main Tera Hero
Home.description: Seenu and Sunaina fall in love with each other when he saves her from a corrupt policeman who wishes to marry her. Meanwhile, Ayesha, a girl Seenu meets on a train journey, wants to marry him.

Home.name: Dream Girl
Home.description: Karamveer gets a job at a call centre due to his ability to talk in a woman's voice. He garners a big fan following but soon gets in trouble with his overzealous clients.

Home.name: Zero
Home.description: Bauua, a person of short stature, falls in love with Aafia, a scientist suffering from cerebral palsy, but soon breaks up with her. Later, what he learns of Aafia changes his life forever.

Home.name: Trainwreck
Home.description: A young magazine writer is made to believe that relationships and marriages hold no value. However, a chance meeting with a sports doctor forces her to rethink her principles.

Home.name: The Other Woman
Home.description: Carly, Mark's girlfriend, is shocked when she learns of his marriage. She meets his wife, Kate, and they become good friends. However, Kate discovers Mark's affair with AMBer.

Home.name: Clueless
Home.description: Cher is a rich high-school student who is learning to cope with adolescence and its problems. She also helps a new student gain popularity and in the process discovers her own feelings for someone.

Home.name: Lucky
Home.description: A 90-year-old atheist has outlived and out-smoked his contemporaries, and as he comes to terms with his own mortality, he searches for ever-elusive enlightenment.

Home.name: My Neighbor's Wife
Home.description: My Neighbor's Wife is a 2011 Filipino drama film directed by Jun Lana, starring Dennis Trillo, Lovi Poe, Jake Cuenca, and Carla Abellana. The film premiered nationwide on SepteMBer 14, 2011 under the distribution of Regal Films.

Home.name: The Mitchells vs. the Machines
Home.description: The Mitchells, a dysfunctional family, must fight a robot apocalypse amidst their much-awaited road trip to save humanity.

Home.name: Go Goa Gone
Home.description: While in Goa, three friends decide to visit an isolated island for a rave party. But the next morning they find themselves not only stranded but also surrounded and hunted by flesh-eating Zombies.

Home.name: Natpuna Ennanu Theriyuma
Home.description: Natpuna Ennanu Theriyuma is a 2019 Indian Tamil-language comedy film directed by Shiva Aravind. The film stars Kavin, Raju Jeyamohan, Arunraja Kamaraj and Remya NaMBeesan while Azhagam Perumal and Ilavarasu play supporting roles. The music was composed by Dharan with editing by Nirmal and cinematography by Yuva.

Home.name: The Family Man
Home.description: Jack's lavish, fast-paced lifestyle changes one Christmas night when he stuMBles into a grocery store holdup and disarms the gunman. The next morning he wakes up in bed lying next to Kate (Tea Leoni), his college sweetheart he left in order to pursue his career, and to the horrifying discovery that his former life no longer exists. As he stuMBles through this alternate suburban universe, Jack finds himself at a crossroad where he must choose between his high-power career and the woman he loves.

Home.name: Batti Gul Meter Chalu
Home.description: The lives of three childhood friends, SK, Lalita and Sundar, take a shocking turn after Sundar's printing press receives an extremely inflated electricity bill.

Home.name: Popcorn
Home.description: Kinder comes to Kerala in search of the woman he loves. His mission takes a new turn when he meets Sharon, who is in search of her absconding boyfriend.

Home.name: Jatts in Golmaal
Home.description: When Titu, a gangster, realises that he needs a heart transplant, he approaches Sunny, a jobless simpleton who desperately wants to go to Canada.

Home.name: Jihne Mera Dil Luteya
Home.description: The story revolves around Yuvraj and Gurnoor who fall for the same girl, Noor. Does Noor love anyone of the two or is it some third person in the picture?

Home.name: Minions (Hindi)
Home.description: Minions Kevin, Stuart and Bob decide to find a new master. They eMBark on a global trip and meet Scarlett Overkill, a female super-villain who recruits them and hatches a plan to take over the world.

Home.name: Ice Age: Dawn Of The Dinosaurs
Home.description: Manny and Ellie are expecting their first child, while Diego plans to move out. Meanwhile, Sid invites trouble by stealing some dinosaur eggs, causing the others to come and save him.

Home.name: De Dana Dan
Home.description: Two penniless friends are in desperate need of money in order to marry their respective girlfriends. In their attempts to make quick money, they kidnap a rich woman's pet and demand a hefty ransom.

Home.name: Little Man
Home.description: Darryl and Vanessa adopt a dwarf, Calvin, when he is found at their doorstep. Little do they know that Calvin is actually a thief who has stolen a diamond and has hidden it in Vanessa's bag.

Home.name: A Haunted House
Home.description: Young couple Malcolm (Marlon Wayans) and Kisha (Essence Atkins) have just moved into their dream home. As they settle in, they learn that they're not alone -- not because the house is haunted, but because Kisha is possessed by a demon. Desperate to salvage his relationship -- and more importantly -- his sex life -- Malcolm hires a coterie of paranormal specialists, which includes a priest and ghost busters, to banish the unwelcome intruder from Kisha's body.

Home.name: Kingsman: The Golden Circle
Home.description: After the enemies blow up their headquarters, the surviving agents of Kingsman band together with their American counterpart to take down a ruthless drug cartel.

Home.name: About Schmidt
Home.description: A newly retired Warren Schmidt forces himself into seclusion after his wife suddenly dies. Faced with the prospect of an uncertain future, he sets out to postpone the marriage of his daughter.

Home.name: Problem Child
Home.description: Ben Healy and his wife decide to adopt Junior, a seven-year-old boy, when they are unable to conceive. Soon, Junior reveals his mischievous nature that drives his adoptive parents crazy.

Home.name: Thunder Force
Home.description: Two childhood best friends reunite as an unlikely crime-fighting superhero duo when one invents a formula that gives ordinary people superpowers.

Home.name: Velle
Home.description: A school principal's daughter and her gang of high school friends lead carefree lives full of mischief. However, when she's warned away from the others by her father, the group decides to teach him a lesson.

Home.name: The Little Hours
Home.description: Massetto poses as a man with hearing and speech impairment in order to seek refuge in a convent full of sexually frustrated nuns. The nuns resist temptation while he struggles to pretend.

Home.name: The Package
Home.description: When four teenage friends go on a camping trip during spring break, an unfortunate accident sets off a race against time to save one's most prized possession.

Home.name: Modern Love
Home.description: Stories that explore the good, the bad, and the ugly aspects of romantic relationships in modern times.

Home.name: Mo
Home.description: Three friends fool people into believing they are exorcists and take money from them under false pretences. But when they get hired to scare a business rival, they encounter a real spirit.

Home.name: The Perfect Match
Home.description: Charlie (Terrence J) is a charming playboy who doesn't believe in serious relationships. His best friends bet him that if he commits to one woman for one month, he's bound to fall in love. Charlie accepts the seemingly easy challenge, but wasn't expecting to cross paths with the beautiful and mysterious Eva (Cassie Ventura). When Charlie coaxes her into a casual affair, Eva turns the tables on him, forcing the lifelong bachelor to question whether he wants more than just a one-night stand.

Home.name: Fukrey Returns
Home.description: After getting Bholi Punjaban arrested, life goes smoothly for Hunny, Choocha, Zafar, and Lali. However, their lives turn upside down when she gets an early bail and comes after them for revenge.

Home.name: Baywatch
Home.description: Lifeguard Mitch Buchannon and his team discover a drug racket involving businesswoman Victoria Leeds and decide to unearth the truth and bring the perpetrators to justice.

Home.name: Ride Along
Home.description: Ben, a security guard, is in love with police officer James Payton's sister. In order to win his future brother-in-law's heart, Ben rides along with him on a 24-hour patrol trip to Atlanta.

Home.name: Taekwondo
Home.description: A man invites a training partner to spend time in his country house among other male friends. Without their girlfriends, they talk of their desires and strengthen their individual bonds.

Home.name: Hotel Transylvania 3: Summer Vacation
Home.description: Count Dracula feels lonely and depressed while running his hotel for monsters. To show him a good time, his family books a luxury vacation cruise exclusively for monsters.

Home.name: The Star
Home.description: Bo, a donkey, is bored of his regular life and wants to do something different. He sets on an adventurous journey where he meets Ruth, a sheep, and Dave, a duck, who make his journey worthwhile.

Home.name: Rush Hour
Home.description: When a Chinese consul's young daughter is kidnapped, Hong Kong Detective Lee must team up with Carter, a loud-mouthed LA detective. Distinctive work styles and cultural differences pose hiccups.

Home.name: Jarugandi
Home.description: To help Sathya and Paari, Gajendran offers them money in return for helping him unite with his lover, Keerthy. However, Sathya ends up kidnapping Keerthy and angers a notorious human trafficker.

Home.name: Hindi Medium
Home.description: Raj and Mita yearn to get Pia, their daughter, educated from a reputed school. When they learn that their background is holding her back, they do everything to ensure that she gets into the school.

Home.name: The Wedding Party
Home.description: As their big day arrives, a couple's lavish wedding plans turn into a nightmare that includes exes, fighting parents and uninvited guests.

Home.name: Half Ticket
Home.description: Vijay decides to leave his house when his father forces him to get married. He wants to start a new life in Bombay, so he pretends to be a child in order to obtain a train ticket.

Home.name: Aa Drushya
Home.description: Surya Tejas, a retired policeman, narrates the details of a case that he investigated years ago to a former colleague's son. In the process, he reveals what really happened on the day of the crime.

Home.name: Love Mocktail
Home.description: After rescuing a woman, Adi reminisces about his love life and tells her about all the heartbreaks he endured in his quest to find his true love.

Home.name: Roberrt
Home.description: Raghava, the head cook in a catering unit, leads a peaceful life with his son Arjun. However, their bliss is short-lived as Raghava's past comes back to haunt him.

Home.name: 1st Rank Raju (Kannada)
Home.description: Raju, an engineering student who is immersed in studies and has little interest in anything else, is forced to come to terms with practicality and faces many challenges as he learns life lessons.

Home.name: Pushpa: The Rise (Kannada)
Home.description: Violence erupts between red sandalwood smugglers and the police charged with bringing down their organization.

Home.name: Jai Bhim (Tamil,Telugu)
Home.description: A pregnant woman from a primitive tribal community, searches desperately for her husband, who is missing from police custody. A High Court advocate rises in support to find her husband and seek justice for them.

Home.name: Pogaru
Home.description: A local thug stands up against the atrocities committed on common people and fights to secure justice for them, thus earning the public's respect and affection.

Home.name: Kalpana
Home.description: Raghava, who fears the dark and is afraid of ghosts, gets possessed by three spirits who want him to take revenge on their murderer.

Home.name: Naduve Antaravirali
Home.description: Sanjay and Nitya fall in love with each other despite facing opposition from their peers. They soon become intimate and Nitya gets pregnant, which causes problems in their lives.

Home.name: Yajamana
Home.description: Krishna, the son-in-law of the village head, tries to defend his village by fighting against a cruel criminal disguised as a business tycoon, Devi Shetty.

Home.name: Amma I Love You
Home.description: On the advice of a saint, a rich man crosses all boundaries to restore his mother's health as she is on her deathbed. In order to do that, he must turn into a beggar for 48 hours.

Home.name: Garuda Gamana Vrishabha Vahana
Home.description: Two childhood friends rise to criminal prominence together until ego, Ambition and jealousy pit them against each other.

Home.name: Dia
Home.description: Dia takes three years to confess her feelings to Rohith but after a terrible accident, she is told he does not survive. Later, when she starts seeing Adi, she finds out that Rohith is still alive.

Home.name: Yuvarathnaa
Home.description: Due to the privatisation of the education sector, RK College is on the verge of closing. However, the principal and a student join hands to prevent it from happening.

Home.name: The Villain
Home.description: Ramu, a commoner, sets out to unite his estranged brother, Rama, with their mother. However, Rama, now known as Ravana, is a mafia don and makes it difficult for Ramu to reach out to him.

Home.name: Hebbuli
Home.description: After Ram's brother dies suddenly, he decides to investigate the reason behind his death. However, he must fight against the corrupt system to protect his family and find the truth.

Home.name: Tagaru
Home.description: Shiva, an encounter specialist, takes an oath to eradicate the wrongdoers from society. Meanwhile, Punarvasu, a young woman, falls in love with him.

Home.name: Rustum
Home.description: ACP Abhishek Bhargav is determined to find the culprits behind the death of his friend, DCP Bharath. His investigation takes him to Bangalore, where he uncovers revelations of an organ trade mafia.

Home.name: Nagarahavu
Home.description: Naganika's family is in charge of an ancient monument that Kapali has his eyes set on. When Kapali kills her to seek the monument, Naganika is reborn as a snake in her next life to seek revenge.

Home.name: RX Soori
Home.description: A young gangster becomes infamous for his criminal activities in Andhra Pradesh. But things change when he falls in love with his childhood friend.

Home.name: Kataka
Home.description: Kumar leaves the town and travels to his native village to open a school for the less fortunate children. However, he faces many obstacles in his quest after his daughter touches a cursed object.

Home.name: Mythri
Home.description: Siddarama is one step away from winning a sum of INR one crore in a game show hosted by his favourite actor Puneeth Rajkumar. However, scientist Mahadev Godke attempts to ruin his plans.

Home.name: The Amazing Spider-Man 2
Home.description: Spider-Man eMBarks on a mission to protect his loved ones when OsCorp, owned by his childhood friend Harry Osborn, unleashes a slew of genetically-modified villains against him.

Home.name: Spider-Man: Far from Home
Home.description: Peter Parker, the beloved superhero Spider-Man, faces four destructive elemental monsters while on holiday in Europe. Soon, he receives help from Mysterio, a fellow hero with mysterious origins.

Home.name: Spider-Man: No Way Home
Home.description: With Spider-Man's identity now revealed, our friendly neighborhood web-slinger is unmasked and no longer able to separate his normal life as Peter Parker from the high stakes of being a superhero. When Peter asks for help from Doctor Strange, the stakes become even more dangerous, forcing him to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.

Home.name: Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse
Home.description: After gaining superpowers from a spider bite, Miles Morales protects the city as Spider-Man. Soon, he meets alternate versions of himself and gets eMBroiled in an epic battle to save the multiverse.

Home.name: Spider-Man 2
Home.description: Peter Parker is dissatisfied with life when he loses his job, the love of his life, Mary Jane, and his powers. Amid all the chaos, he must fight Doctor Octavius who threatens to destroy New York City.

Home.name: Spider-Man: Homecoming
Home.description: Peter Parker tries to stop the Vulture from selling weapons made with advanced Chitauri technology while trying to balance his life as an ordinary high school student.

Home.name: The Amazing Spider-Man
Home.description: Peter Parker, an outcast high school student, gets bitten by a radioactive spider and attains superpowers. Soon, he is forced to use his abilities to fight a monstrous foe.

Home.name: Spider-Man
Home.description: Peter Parker's life changes when he is bitten by a genetically altered spider and gains superpowers. He uses his powers to help people and finds himself facing the Green Goblin, an evil maniac.

Home.name: Spider-Man: No Way Home (Hindi)
Home.description: With Spider-Man's identity now revealed, our friendly neighborhood web-slinger is unmasked and no longer able to separate his normal life as Peter Parker from the high stakes of being a superhero. When Peter asks for help from Doctor Strange, the stakes become even more dangerous, forcing him to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.

Home.name: Spider-Man (Hindi)
Home.description: Peter Parker's life changes when he is bitten by a genetically altered spider and gains superpowers. He uses his powers to help people and finds himself facing the Green Goblin, an evil maniac.

Home.name: The Amazing Spider-Man 2 (Hindi)
Home.description: Spider-Man eMBarks on a mission to protect his loved ones when OsCorp, owned by his childhood friend Harry Osborn, unleashes a slew of genetically-modified villains against him.

Home.name: Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse (Hindi)
Home.description: After gaining superpowers from a spider bite, Miles Morales protects the city as Spider-Man. Soon, he meets alternate versions of himself and gets eMBroiled in an epic battle to save the multiverse.

Home.name: Spider-Man: Far from Home (Hindi)
Home.description: Peter Parker, the beloved superhero Spider-Man, faces four destructive elemental monsters while on holiday in Europe. Soon, he receives help from Mysterio, a fellow hero with mysterious origins.

Home.name: Spider-Man: Homecoming (Telugu/Tamil)
Home.description: Peter Parker tries to stop the Vulture from selling weapons made with advanced Chitauri technology while trying to balance his life as an ordinary high school student.

Home.name: Spider-Man 3
Home.description: Peter Parker becomes one with a syMBiotic alien that bolsters his Spider-Man avatar and affects his psyche. He also has to deal with Sandman and maintain a fragmented relationship with Mary Jane.

Home.name: Fast X
Home.description: Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto and his family have outsmarted and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they must confront the most lethal opponent they've ever faced. Fueled by revenge, a terrifying threat emerges from the shadows of the past to shatter Dom's world and destroy everything -- and everyone -- he loves.

Home.name: Finding Nemo
Home.description: After his son gets abducted from the Great Barrier Reef and is dispatched to Sydney, Marlin, a meek clownfish, enlists the help of a forgetful fish and embarks on a journey to bring him home.

Home.name: IB 71
Home.description: An Indian intelligence service must prevent a terrorist attack in this high-stakes Hindi-language thriller. Moments of threat are frequent but fight sequences are restrained with limited injury detail.

Home.name: Knights of the Zodiac
Home.description: When a headstrong street orphan unwittingly taps into hidden powers, he discovers he might be the only person alive who can protect a reincarnated goddess who was sent to watch over humanity.

Home.name: Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3
Home.description: Still reeling from the loss of Gamora, Peter Quill must rally his team to defend the universe and protect one of their own. If the mission is not completely successful, it could possibly lead to the end of the Guardians as we know them.

Home.name: Ant-Man and the Wasp
Home.description: Despite being under house arrest, Scott Lang, along with the Wasp, sets out to help Dr Hank Pym to enter the quantum realm as they face new enemies along the way.

Home.name: Ravanasura
Home.description: ACP Hanumanth Rao, a police officer, investigates a few brutal murders and zeroes in on junior criminal lawyer Ravindra, who, under his goofy exterior, harbours a secret penchant for murder.

Home.name: The Super Mario Bros. Movie
Home.description: With help from Princess Peach, Mario gets ready to square off against the all-powerful Bowser to stop his plans from conquering the world.

Home.name: Mad Max: Fury Road
Home.description: In a post-apocalyptic wasteland, Max, a drifter and survivor, unwillingly joins Imperator Furiosa, a rebel warrior, in a quest to overthrow a tyrant who controls the land's water supply.

Home.name: Chengiz
Home.description: Chengiz: The One Who Has No Boundaries No Limits; simply known as Chengiz is a 2023 Indian Bengali-language period action thriller film co-written and directed by Rajesh Ganguly from a story written by Neeraj Pandey and himself. It is produced by Jeet, Gopal Madnani and Amit Jumrani.

Home.name: Pokemon the Movie: I Choose You!
Home.description: Ash Ketchum from Pallet Town is 10 years old today. This means he is now old enough to become a Pokmon Trainer. Ash dreams big about the adventures he will experience after receiving his first Pokmonfrom Professor Oak.

Home.name: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom
Home.description: Indiana Jones, a legendary archaeologist, finds himself in India, where a bunch of poor villagers reaches out to him to track down an ancient stone that has been stolen by an evil priest.

Home.name: Ghosted
Home.description: Ghosted is a 2023 American romantic action-adventure comedy film directed by Dexter Fletcher and written by Rhett Reese, Paul Wernick, Chris McKenna, and Erik Sommers, from a story by Reese and Wernick. The film stars Chris Evans and Ana de Armas.

Home.name: Ice Age
Home.description: Manny the mammoth, Sid the loquacious sloth, and Diego the sabre-toothed tiger go on a comical quest to return a human baby back to his father, across a world on the brink of an ice age.

Home.name: Ice Age: Collision Course
Home.description: Scrat accidentally sets off an asteroid to Earth while trying to get his acorn. However, Manny, Sid and Diego must join forces with Buck to prevent the asteroid from wiping out their existence.

Home.name: Gumraah
Home.description: Gumraah is a 2023 Indian Hindi-language crime thriller film directed by Vardhan Ketkar and produced by T-Series Films and Murad Khetani's Cine1 Studios. The film stars Aditya Roy Kapur, in a dual role along with Mrunal Thakur and Ronit Roy. It is a remake of the 2019 Tamil film Thadam.

Home.name: Gladiator
Home.description: Commodus takes over power and demotes Maximus, one of the preferred generals of his father, Emperor Marcus Aurelius. As a result, Maximus is relegated to fighting till death as a gladiator.

Home.name: Supercell
Home.description: In order to follow the footsteps of his father who was a legendary storm chaser, a teenage boy leaves his mother and runs away from his home.

Home.name: Passengers
Home.description: During a voyage to a distant planet, Jim's hypersleep pod malfunctions which wakes him up. So, he and fellow passenger work together to prevent their spaceship from meeting with a disaster.

Home.name: Snow White and the Huntsman
Home.description: Queen Ravenna, an evil woman, tasks Eric, a huntsman, with murdering Snow White, her stepdaughter. Instead of killing her, he ends up becoming her protector.

Home.name: XXX
Home.description: The US government recruits extreme sports athlete Xander Cage to infiltrate a Russian criminal ring, which is plotting the destruction of the world.

Home.name: Perfect Addiction
Home.description: When a successful MMA trainer discovers that her boyfriend, the reigning champion, has been cheating on her, she sets out to get revenge by training the one man capable of dethroning him: his arch-nemesis. What begins as payback quickly turns into a complicated and steamy love triangle.

Home.name: Bholaa
Home.description: After 10 years of imprisonment, Bholaa is finally going home to meet his young daughter. However, his journey is not so simple as he soon faces a pathway full of crazy obstacles, with death lurking around every corner.

Home.name: Ponniyin Selvan: I
Home.description: Sensing an uprising in the capital, Crown Prince Aditha Karikalan sends his friend Vallavaraiyan Vandiyadevan on a mission that sets off a series of conspiracies against the reigning king.

Home.name: Karnasubarner Guptodhon
Home.description: Karnasubarner Guptodhon is an Indian Bengali adventure thriller film directed by Dhrubo Banerjee and produced by Shrikant Mohta and Mahendra Soni. It is a sequel to Durgeshgorer Guptodhon and the third film in Sona Da franchise.

Home.name: Star Wars: The Clone Wars
Home.description: As more star systems get swept into the Clone Wars, the valiant Jedi knights struggle to maintain order. Anakin Skywalker and his Padawan learner Ahsoka Tano embark on a mission that brings them face-to-face with Jabba the Hutt. Plotting against them is evil Count Dooku and his agent, Asajj Ventress, who would ensure that the Jedis fail. Meanwhile, Yoda and Obi-Wan Kenobi lead the clone army against the forces of the Dark Side.

Home.name: Ponniyin Selvan: I
Home.description: Sensing an uprising in the capital, Crown Prince Aditha Karikalan sends his friend Vallavaraiyan Vandiyadevan on a mission that sets off a series of conspiracies against the reigning king.

Home.name: SHAZAM! FURY OF THE GODS
Home.description: Bestowed with the powers of the gods, Billy Batson and his fellow foster kids are still learning how to juggle teenage life with their adult superhero alter egos. When a vengeful trio of ancient gods arrives on Earth in search of the magic stolen from them long ago, Shazam and his allies get thrust into a battle for their superpowers, their lives, and the fate of the world.

Home.name: The Rookies
Home.description: An extreme sports athlete joins a mysterious special agent and her ragtag team of recruits to battle a group of deadly terrorists.

Home.name: The Space Between Us
Home.description: Sarah Elliot, an astronaut, dies on Mars while giving birth to her son. The boy visits Earth and starts searching for his father with the help of a clever girl.

Home.name: Kabzaa
Home.description: Kabzaa is a 2023 Indian Kannada-language period action thriller film directed by R. Chandru. The film features Upendra, Shiva Rajkumar, Kiccha Sudeepa and Shriya Saran in the lead roles. Kabzaa was released on 17 March 2023 in Kannada, along with the dubbed versions of Tamil, Telugu, Hindi and Malayalam.

Home.name: The Siege
Home.description: International assassin Walker is compromised during a mission and sent to a reassignment center for a new identity. During his stay at the facility, a ruthless assault team storms the compound searching for someone their boss has lost. Walker begrudgingly falls in with skilled hitwoman Elda and her mysterious ward Juliet in order to survive the night.

Home.name: Karthikeya 2
Home.description: Trapped in a web of conspiracies and betrayal, Karthikeya, a doctor, must retrieve a mythological treasure and clear his name.

Home.name: Batman Forever
Home.description: Batman must stop Two-Face who seeks revenge from him after a courtroom accident leaves him disfigured on one side and The Riddler who has a nefarious plan of his own.

Home.name: All Is Lost
Home.description: shipping container. With his scanty supplies depleting, the sailor

Home.name: Doraemon: Nobita's new dinosaur
Home.description: Doraemon: Nobita's New Dinosaur is a Japanese animated science fiction adventure film, and the first Doraemon film to be released during the Reiwa era. It celebrates 50 years of the Doraemon franchise, alongside Stand by Me Doraemon 2.

Home.name: Daman
Home.description: DAMaN, abbreviation for Durgama Anchalare Malaria Nirakarana, is a 2022 Indian Odia-language adventure drama film written and directed by Vishal Mourya and Debi Prasad Lenka and produced by Deependra Samal. The film stars Babushaan Mohanty and Dipanwit Dashmohapatra in lead roles.

Home.name: Black Adam
Home.description: After being bestowed with godly powers and imprisoned for it, Black Adam is liberated from his earthly binds to unleash his fury on the modern world.

Home.name: Mojin: The Worm Valley
Home.description: Legendary explorer Hu Bayi searches for the tomb of Emperor Xian on an island of monstrous creatures.

Home.name: Phineas and Ferb the Movie: Across the 2nd Dimension
Home.description: Phineas and Ferb enter an alternate dimension where Doofenshmirtz rules the tri-state area. They must find a way back home with the help of Perry, who they learn is a secret agent.

Home.name: Ant-Man and the Wasp: Quantumania
Home.description: Ant-Man and the Wasp find themselves exploring the Quantum Realm, interacting with strange new creatures and embarking on an adventure that pushes them beyond the limits of what they thought was possible.

Home.name: Everest
Home.description: Two groups, one led by Rob Hall and the other by Scott Fischer, encounter several challenges and threatening weather conditions as they attempt to scale Mount Everest.

Home.name: Malikappuram
Home.description: Eight-year-old Kallu from Panchalimedu village desperately wants to visit Sabarimala.

Home.name: Puss in Boots: The Last Wish
Home.description: Puss in Boots discovers that his passion for adventure has taken its toll: he has burnt through eight of his nine lives. Puss sets out on an epic journey to find the mythical Last Wish and restore his nine lives.

Home.name: Black Panther: Wakanda Forever
Home.description: Queen Ramonda, Shuri, M'Baku, Okoye and the Dora Milaje fight to protect their nation from intervening world powers in the wake of King T'Challa's death. As the Wakandans strive to embrace their next chapter, the heroes must band together with Nakia and Everett Ross to forge a new path for their beloved kingdom.

Home.name: Lakadbaggha
Home.description: An animal loving vigilante Arjun Bakshi, unearths the fact that an underground illegal animal trade cell functions from Kolkata port. On investigating he chances upon a rare species of the Indian Striped Hyena (Lakadbaggha). 8.9/10. 396. Victor Mukherjee.

Home.name: Veera Simha Reddy
Home.description: Veera Simha Reddy is a 2023 Indian Telugu-language action drama film written and directed by Gopichand Malineni and produced by Mythri Movie Makers. It stars Nandamuri Balakrishna in a dual role along with Honey Rose, Shruti Haasan, Varalaxmi Sarathkumar and Duniya Vijay.

Home.name: Kuttey
Home.description: One rainy night in the outskirts of Mumbai, three stray gangs unknowingly cross paths on the hunt and it's every man for himself.

Home.name: An Action Hero
Home.description: After getting caught up in an accident while filming in Haryana, icon Maanav now lives in hiding.

Home.name: Uunchai
Home.description: Three friends leave their cozy lives behind to embark on a journey to Mount Everest.

Home.name: Ram Setu
Home.description: An atheist archaeologist turned believer races against time to prove the true existence of the legendary Ram Setu before evil forces destroy the pillar of India's heritage.

Home.name: Lightyear
Home.description: Legendary space ranger Buzz Lightyear embarks on an intergalactic adventure alongside ambitious recruits Izzy, Mo, Darby, and his robot companion, Sox. As this motley crew tackles their toughest mission yet, they must learn to work together as a team to escape the evil Zurg and his dutiful robot army that are never far behind.

Home.name: DC League of Super-Pets
Home.description: When Superman and the rest of the league get kidnapped by Lex Luthor, it is up to Superdog Krypto to rescue them. He finds a group of shelter pets with superpowers and convinces them to help him.

Home.name: Slumberland
Home.description: A young girl discovers a secret map to the dreamworld of Slumberland, and with the help of an eccentric outlaw, she traverses dreams and flees nightmares, with the hope that she will be able to see her late father again.

Home.name: Brahmastra: Part One  Shiva
Home.description: A young man on the brink of falling in love gets his world turned upside down when he discovers he has the power to control fire and a connection to a secret society of guardians.

Home.name: Top Gun: Maverick
Home.description: Thirty years of service leads Maverick to train a group of elite TOPGUN graduates to prepare for a high-profile mission while Maverick battles his past demons.

Home.name: Shamshera
Home.description: In an attempt to save his tribe, Shamshera is killed by Shudh Singh and termed a traitor. Years later, his son decides to take revenge and reunite his tribe.

Home.name: Mia and the White Lion
Home.description: Mia moves to South Africa with her family to manage a lion farm and develops a special bond with Charlie, a white lion cub. However, things change when she uncovers her father's secret.

Home.name: HIT: The First Case
Home.description: Vikram is a 32-year-old cop. While he is battling with his own traumatic past, the stakes get high when a girl called Preethi mysteriously disappears in Hyderabad and Vikram has to solve the case at any cost.

Home.name: The Adventures of Tintin
Home.description: Tintin, a young reporter, buys the model of a ship and is intrigued when his dog shows him a scroll after the toy breaks. He tells Captain Haddock and they embark on an adventure to find a shipwreck.

Home.name: The Sea Beast
Home.description: The life of a legendary sea monster hunter is turned upside down when a young girl stows away on his ship.

Home.name: Jaws
Home.description: A police chief, a marine scientist and a fisherman spring into action after a white shark terrorises the inhabitants of Amity, a quiet island.

Home.name: Thor: Love and Thunder
Home.description: Thor eMBarks on a journey unlike anything he's ever faced -- a quest for inner peace. However, his retirement gets interrupted by Gorr the God Butcher, a galactic killer who seeks the extinction of the gods.

Home.name: Minions: The Rise of Gru
Home.description: In the 1970s, young Gru tries to join a group of supervillains called the Vicious 6 after they oust their leader -- the legendary fighter Wild Knuckles. When the interview turns disastrous, Gru and his Minions go on the run with the Vicious 6 hot on their tails. Luckily, he finds an unlikely source for guidance -- Wild Knuckles himself -- and soon discovers that even bad guys need a little help from their friends.

Home.name: The Avengers
Home.description: Nick Fury is compelled to launch the Avengers Initiative when Loki poses a threat to planet Earth. His squad of superheroes put their minds together to accomplish the task.

Home.name: The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King
Home.description: The former Fellowship meMBers prepare for the final battle. While Frodo and Sam approach Mount Doom to destroy the One Ring, they follow Gollum, unaware of the path he is leading them to.

Home.name: Aquaman

Home.name: Man of Steel
Home.description: Clark learns about the source of his abilities and his real home when he enters a Kryptonian ship in the Artic. However, an old enemy follows him to Earth in search of a codex and brings destruction.

Home.name: Minnal Murali
Home.description: A tailor gains special powers after being struck by lightning, but must take down an unexpected foe if he is to become the superhero his hometown needs.

Home.name: Snake eye
Home.description: An ancient Japanese clan called the Arashikage welcomes tenacious loner Snake Eyes after he saves the life of their heir apparent. Upon arrival in Japan, the Arashikage teach him the ways of the ninja warrior while also providing him something he's been longing for: a home. However, when secrets from Snake Eyes' past are revealed, his honor and allegiance get tested -- even if that means losing the trust of those closest to him.

Home.name: The Amazing Spider-Man 2
Home.description: Spider-Man eMBarks on a mission to protect his loved ones when OsCorp, owned by his childhood friend Harry Osborn, unleashes a slew of genetically-modified villains against him.

Home.name: 100% Wolf
Home.description: Freddy Lupin comes from a proud family line of werewolves. Positive he'll become the most fearsome werewolf ever, Freddy is in for a shock when his first warfing goes awry, turning him into a ferocious poodle.

Home.name: Venom: Let There Be Carnage (Venom 2) (English)
Home.description: Eddie Brock is still struggling to coexist with the shape-shifting extraterrestrial Venom. When deranged serial killer Cletus Kasady also becomes host to an alien syMBiote, Brock and Venom must put aside their differences to stop his reign of terror.

Home.name: No Time To Die
Home.description: James Bond is enjoying a tranquil life in Jamaica after leaving active service. However, his peace is short-lived as his old CIA friend, Felix Leiter, shows up and asks for help. The mission to rescue a kidnapped scientist turns out to be far more treacherous than expected, leading Bond on the trail of a mysterious villain who's armed with a dangerous new technology.

Home.name: The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies (English)
Home.description: Bilbo fights against a nuMBer of enemies to save the life of his Dwarf friends and protects the Lonely Mountain after a conflict arises.

Home.name: Free Guy
Home.description: When a bank teller discovers he's actually a background player in an open-world video game, he decides to become the hero of his own story -- one that he can rewrite himself. In a world where there's no limits, he's determined to save the day his way before it's too late, and maybe find a little romance with the coder who conceived him.

Home.name: Spider-Man: Far from Home
Home.description: Peter Parker, the beloved superhero Spider-Man, faces four destructive elemental monsters while on holiday in Europe. Soon, he receives help from Mysterio, a fellow hero with mysterious origins.

Home.name: Spider-Man: No Way Home
Home.description: With Spider-Man's identity now revealed, our friendly neighborhood web-slinger is unmasked and no longer able to separate his normal life as Peter Parker from the high stakes of being a superhero. When Peter asks for help from Doctor Strange, the stakes become even more dangerous, forcing him to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.

Home.name: Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides
Home.description: Captain Jack Sparrow sets sail in search of the legendary fountain of youth. His mission puts him up against a mysterious woman from his past, an old enemy Barbossa and the feared pirate, Blackbeard.

Home.name: The mummy
Home.description: Adventurer Rick O'Connell and Egyptologist Evelyn, along with a bunch of archaeologists, inadvertently wake up an evil mummy during an archaeological excavation at the ancient city of Hamunaptra.

Home.name: Captain America: Civil War

Home.name: Mulan

Home.description: Raj, a vet from MuMBai, arrives at his father's elephant reserve for his mother's 10th death anniversary. However, things change after he is pitted in a war against the poachers.

Jaguar Paw (Rudy YounGBlood), a peaceful hunter in a remote tribe, is captured along with his entire village in a raid. He is scheduled for a ritual sacrifice until he makes a daring escape and tries to make it back to his pregnant wife and son.

Home.description: Peter Parker is dissatisfied with life when he loses his job, the love of his life, Mary Jane, and his powers. Amid all the chaos, he must fight Doctor Octavius who threatens to destroy New York City.

Home.description: Peter Parker tries to stop the Vulture from selling weapons made with advanced Chitauri technology while trying to balance his life as an ordinary high school student.
